\id REV - Ekajuk New Testament
\h Ellennge
\toc1 Ellennge
\toc2 Ell
\mt2 NSOL NYI ESOWO LENNGE
\mt1 KA JON
\c 1
\nb 
\v 1 Nwer nyia bo nyono nsol nyi Jisos Kraist lennge no, nyi Esowo ka-e no re á tib alokeltum ebe, eji bo lꞌkahn ji bahke gulu ellimi. Jisos jo tumu enjel tv nlokeltum ewe Jon, á jo ba lennge nsol nyio ka-e,
\v 2 Jon jio ji jo yiimi ntianse ka alum Esowo, fere jo yiimi ntianse ka etingitingi ji Jisos Kraist bungu no, a nsol kpee nyi á nyehne no.
\v 3 Elfuulu bahke jolo ka nne no lꞌlung alum nya enyehnamahr ji Esowo. Elfuulu bahke jolo ka ane ba bahke jo wuk alum nya bo nyono no, fere jo bum. Tibre ngare ebkabbe, nyi nsol nyio kpee bahke limi.
\s1 Nnyo mi Jon kake aro na asehma
\p 
\v 4 Me Jon, me wo kp-n kake nnyo, wahn aro nyao na asehma nya li go Esia. Elfuulu, a elkoono jol a nahne, ni lohng goji Esowo bi li anv, bꞌnehm o bi jolo mahne mahne, bꞌnehm o bi bahke kpe feere ba, elfuulu, a elkoono ni lohng goji atohko nyao na asehma nya yim go mbuksong eti etul ji Esowo,
\v 5 ni tob lohng goji Jisos Kraist ji jolo ntianse nyi bele ekakesehk,\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Jon 18:34,37\f* ye ji li ngbokambang a nne no nyahme go elkv. Ye wo li ntul no atem atul ba li go njini nyia.
\p Ye wo li nne no e kor-e no, no ma lim re, wahr for go egahre abꞌbi tib go ege alung,
\v 6 fere lim-r re wahr jol atul, fere jol abalimajom ba Esowo Nde.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft 1 Pit 2:5,9\f* Nong, ellub jol ka-e, a nsahm go njinanjini.
\q1 
\v 7 Á bahke gulu elbake go akparesemsem.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Elt 1:11\f*
\q1 Nne awohng awohng bahk-e nyehne, budu ane bao ba jahm-e elkong.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Jon 19:34,37\f*
\q1 Ye wo bahke wahnge nnahb anyehng anyehng nyi li go njini bahke kehme ellingi ndon ndon.
\q1 Bahke jolo ano. Emen.
\q1 
\v 8 Jehova no gbale sehng, no li anv, nonehm no jolo mahne mahne, nonehm no bahke kpe feere ba,\f + \fr 1:8 \ft Hib 13:8\f*
\q1 á kpꞌbungu re, “Me wo li Alfa, me wo li Omega.” (Ji lohngo re, mbomannahb, a esꞌkohlo.)
\s1 Ana Jon nyehne Kraist
\p 
\v 9 Me wo li Jon mmonanne ejahne ji kpꞌtob nyehn erem a nahne, me n tob li etul bꞌnehm bi wahn ma li, fere kpꞌtob kpuumu erem a nahne, eji e li ka Jisos. Bo rod-m rod kak go ejahbe ji li go elka alahb, ji bo kpo lung re Patmos, tib go esi ji alum Esowo nya n jo bung, a ntianse nyi n jo yiimi ka Jisos.
\p 
\v 10 Etingi etohko rod-m rod tahm a name go efung bio bi Jehova.\f + \fr 1:10 \ft 1 Tes 5:2; 2 Pit 3:10\f* N wuku ellum ni bungu wahre wahre go egama njahm, ni jolo ana ntang.
\v 11 Ellum nio bungu re, “Nyon nsol nyi a bahke nyehne, wo kak go nwer, song tum tv aro na asehma, ero bi li go Efesus, a bi li go Smirna, a bi li go Pergamum, a bi li go Tiatira, a bi li go Sardis, a bi li go Filadelfia, go ero bi li go Laodisea.”
\p 
\v 12 N kehm keebe re me n nyehn nne no jo bung a name. Eji n keebe no, n kehm nyehne etꞌrekahng na ebsehma bi bo limi go agul.
\v 13 Go elka elka ni atꞌrekahng nyao, n nyehne ejum yim no go elfoongo ni nne. Á kake ekpawobo ji badd-e tete rehng akpade, fere gbaange egbaange agul go ege ekꞌkv.
\v 14 Esi eje, a alv enye jo bare kparaang. Amahr enye jolo ana eblikagun.
\v 15 Akpade enye jolo ana ekuungu ji li gele gele. Tibre bo kake agun. Ellum ene ni á bungu no jolo are egburu ewahl elahb ji.
\v 16 Á fili elonlo na ebsehma go ege eboblum. Ekahngkahng bi jo kong njahm ebal ebal lohngo go ege a nnyo. Esamahr ebe jo ya ana njul kpo ya daan.
\p 
\v 17 Eji n nyehn-e no, n kehm gboko go ege alata ana nne no ma kpo. Á kehm-m kunu eboblum ebe, kehm bungu re, “Ka fahl, me wo li ngbokambang, me wo li nkahlanjahm.\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Luk 5:8-10\f*
\v 18 Me wo li nne no li go elkpin. N kpꞌkpo, anv, me n noa go elkpin. M bahke jolo ano ano go njinanjini. Me wo, elkv wob go egame ebo. Me wo kpi ejahbe akvne.
\v 19 Jo nyon nsol nyi a ma nyehn, nsol nyi li anv, a nsol nyi bahke limi.
\v 20 Ana wo nkpokosi nyi a nyehne no lohngo no, eji a nyehne elonlo ebsehma go egame eboblum, fere nyehn etꞌrekahng ebsehma. Elonlo ebsehma bio lohngo enjel nya aro nyao na asehma. Etꞌrekahng ebsehma bio lohngo aro asehma nyao.”
\c 2
\s1 Etib bi Jon tiingi tv ero bi Efesus
\p 
\v 1 “Nyon tv enjel nyi ero bi Efesus re, Alum nya ana, nya nne no fili elonlo na ebsehma go eboblum yahke bung, ye ji kpꞌjene go elka elka ni etꞌrekahng na ebsehma bi bo limi go agul. \fig Etꞌrekahng na ebsehma|alt="The seven candle stick" src="lb00277c.tif" size="col" loc="Rev.2:1" ref="2:1"\fig*
\p 
\v 2 “N kpꞌkahne eltum ni a kpꞌlimi, ana a kpꞌbade, jo lim eltum, fere kpꞌkpuumu. N kpꞌkahne re, a nehm jo taame re, abi ane woomo go egahne ellong. Wobwuungu ane bao ba kpo lung elbo re abatiingetib Jisos, na ga, ano sang bo li no.\f + \fr 2:2 \ft 1 Jon 4:1\f* Wobseb kahn re, bo akimfahnge nya.
\v 3 Wobnyehn erem go egame esi, fere kpuumu. Eltum wa tikem kpen.
\p 
\v 4 “Ejum ji ana, ji n kpi bada na. Tibre, wa n nehme kpe kor ana wuku wuku n jo kor-a.\f + \fr 2:4 \ft Mak 12:30-31\f*
\v 5 Gbo ntir, wo nyehn nsol nyi a ma yake bum. Yake mbang nyio, wo fere jo lim mbang nyi wuku wuku a gbo mbang jo lim. A tohko yake mbang nyio, m bahke ba radde etꞌrekahng eja edi ji kun no.\f + \fr 2:5 \ft Luk 12:46\f*
\v 6 Ejum ji ana, ji m bahk-a tehke. Nsol nyi abatꞌtoono ba Nikola kpo lim, kpo sab-a jang jang ana kpo tob sab-m.
\p 
\v 7 “Nne no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk ji Etingi Etohko kpꞌbungu tong aneb ero. Nne no lꞌga anebekv ebe, m bahk-e kake eti jio ji elkpin, á li, ji li go etahngga ji Esowo.\f + \fr 2:7 \ft Ell 22:2\f*
\s1 Etib bi Jon tiingi tv ero bi Smirna
\p 
\v 8 “Nyon tv enjel nyi ero bi Smirna re, Alum nya ana, nya nne no li ngbokambang, a nkahlanjahm yahke bung, ye ji kpo no, á ma fere jol go elkpin.
\p 
\v 9 “N kpꞌkahne erem eba bi a kpꞌnyehne. N kpꞌkahne ana a ma gbo ekpak, jol eji a li li efange nne. N kpꞌkahne abi nsol nya ane ba kpo lung elbo re, ‘Jus’ kpo bung tob-a, na nyehne, Jus sang, bo li ka nnehm.\f + \fr 2:9 \ft 2 Kor 11:14-15\f*
\v 10 Ka fahl erem bi a bahke nyehne! Nnehm yahke rod egom ejahne jindiki kak ngbekobo, eji á lꞌgar-a. Nfung na ewubu nyi a bahke nyehne erem bi ebnohko.\f + \fr 2:10 \ft 2 Tim 3:12\f* Afi jolo go elkv, bel ekakesehk.\f + \fr 2:10 \ft Mat 10:28\f* Owo m bahk-a konngo ekpasi ji elkpin.
\p 
\v 11 “Nne no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk ji Etingi Etohko kpꞌbungu tong aneb ero. Nne no lꞌga anebekv ebe, etoono elkv we nehm kpe lim ejumjum.\f + \fr 2:11 \ft Ell 20:14\f*
\s1 Etib bi Jon tiingi tv ero bi Pergamum
\p 
\v 12 “Nyon tv enjel nyi ero bi Pergamum re,
\p “Alum nya ana, nya nne no kpi ekahngkahng bi kpo kong njahm ebal ebal yahke bung.\f + \fr 2:12 \ft Hib 4:12\f*
\p 
\v 13 “N kpꞌkahne edi ji a lene no. A lene edi ji eti etul ji nnehm li no. Wobyiimi tꞌtahne go egama mbing. A tikem ten mbang enyame, jol ngare nyio nyi bo wulu Antipas ji woomo go egahne ellong, ye ji jolo nkakesehk a ntianse enyame go edi ji nnehm lene no.
\p 
\v 14 “N kpi abon nsol bada na. Egom ejahne jindiki jia ona, ji kpꞌtoono eltibi ni Belam, ji tubu Balahk elle re, á jo lim, eji aneb Israel lꞌjo gbo yel abiafem, fere jo li nsol alehke nyi bo ko jom eblom, fere jo noongo a ane.\f + \fr 2:14 \ft Jud 11\f*
\v 15 Egom ejahne jindiki jia, ji kpꞌtoono eltibi ni abatꞌtoono ba Nikola.
\v 16 Yake mbang nyio! Tohko jol ano, m bahke gulu elbake go ega, ba nok ebta a bo go ekahngkahng bi kpo lohng go egama nnyo.
\p 
\v 17 “Nne no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk ji Etingi Etohko kpꞌbungu tong aneb ero.
\p “Nne no lꞌga anebekv ebe, m bahk-e kake mmanna nyi li go mbiiri, á li. M bahk-e tob ka mbarebare eltal ni bo nyono mbing a nfenfe, nyi nne awohng awohng kil elkahne, sehngem nne no bahke koko eltal nio, ye wo bahke kahne.
\s1 Etib bi Jon tiingi tv ero bi Tiatira
\p 
\v 18 “Nyon tv enjel nyi ero bi Tiatira re,
\p “Alum nya ana, nya Mmon no Esowo no kpi amahr ana eblikagun yahke bung, ye ji akpade enye li ana ekuungu ji li gele gele.
\p 
\v 19 “N kpꞌkahne eltum ena ni a kpꞌlimi, a eltaame ena, a elkoro ena, fere kahn ana a kp-m loko. N kpꞌkahne elkpuumu ena ni a kpo kpuumu. N kpꞌkahne re, anv, a kpꞌlimi sehnge ana wuku wuku a jo lim.
\p 
\v 20 “Ejum ji ana, ji n kpi no bada na. A kpo bulu amahr enya, eji a kpꞌnyehne Jesebel, nnenkal no kpo lung elne re, ‘Nnyehnamahr Esowo’. Á kpo tib, fere jo nehm alokeltum ebame, eji bo lꞌjo noongo a ane, fere jo li nsol alehke nyi bo ko jom eblom.
\v 21 N ka-e ngare re á yake mbang nyio. Á tꞌten re, á nehm sennge njahm go ege enoongo a ane.
\v 22 Owo wahnge m bahk-e rodo tub edilnong, a ane ba kpo noongo a ne. Owo bo bahke nyehne erem bi ga ga, tohko jol re bo gbo ndon go elkohn nsol nyi á kpꞌlimi.
\v 23 M bahke wulu abon ebe. Ano wo bahke wahnge aneb ero kpee kahn re, me wo li nne no kpo rab atahng ma nne. M bahk-n tuuru go nne awohng awohng jang jang ana ń limi no.
\p 
\v 24 “Wahn erik ane ji li go Tiatira, ji kala toono eltibi nio, wahn ji kala kpili nsol nyi ane bandiki kpo lung re, ‘Nsol nyi nnehm nyi li go mbiiri’, n kp-n tongo re, wahn n nehm kpe si elsol nehko.
\v 25 Yiimen tꞌtahne go mbang nyi ń kpꞌtoono, tete me n feere ba.
\p 
\v 26 “Nne no lꞌga anebekv ebe, fere jo lim eltum ename tete rehng go esꞌkohro, ye wo m bahk-e kake nsahm nyi á bahke fili ane baka baka ba ki nyi Esowo.
\v 27 Á bahke jo ko ebti bi bo limi go ekuungu, jo fili bo, fere jo ruumu bo ana nne ruumu atu wa.\f + \fr 2:27 \ft Ell 12:5; 19:14-15\f* Tibre m bahk-e kake nsahm nyꞌnehm nyi m bele goji Nsoo.
\v 28 M bahk-e kake elonlo ji efungfu.\f + \fr 2:28 \ft Ell 22:16\f*
\p 
\v 29 “Nne no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk ji Etingi Etohko kpꞌbungu tong aneb ero.\f + \fr 2:29 \ft Mat 11:15\f*
\c 3
\s1 Etib bi Jon tiingi tv ero bi Sardis
\p 
\v 1 “Nyon tv enjel nyi ero bi Sardis re,
\p “Alum nya ana, nya nne no kpi etohko na ebsehma bi Esowo,\f + \fr 3:1 \ft 1 Tim 5:6; Jems 2:17\f* a elonlo na ebsehma yahke bung.
\p “N kpꞌkahne eltum ena ni a kpꞌlimi. N kpꞌkahne ana bo kpo gahm-a re, wo noa go elkpin, na nyehne ga, wobkpo.
\v 2 Nyahme, wo kak ane bako ebo, ba ma sa, bo ji yahke kpo.\f + \fr 3:2 \ft Jems 5:19-20\f* Tibre eltum ni a ma lim, me n nyehn re, gaam nob go ejang bi Esowo ebame.
\v 3 Buumu alum nya bo tib-a no, wo fere buumu nya a wuku no. Jo bum alum nyao, wo yake mbang enya nyi a kpꞌtoono. A tohko nyahme, m bahke bake go ega ana nwajv. A nehm kahn ngare nyi m bahke bake.\f + \fr 3:3 \ft 1 Tes 5:2\f*
\v 4 Egom ejahne jindiki ji li o Sardis, bo ka nyake awobo ebo.\f + \fr 3:4 \ft Jud 23\f* Bo bahke tiki jo jen a name ano a abarebare nsol, tibre fꞌfuumu re bo lim ano.
\p 
\v 5 “Nne no lꞌga anebekv ebe, bo bahk-e liibi abarebare nsol. N nehm fvvdv mbing enye go nwer nyio nyi elkpin.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Ell 20:15\f* M bahke yiimi ntianse ka-e go esamahr bi Nsoo, a bi enjel enye re, á li ka me.
\p 
\v 6 “Nne no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk ji Etingi Etohko kpꞌbungu tong aneb ero.
\s1 Etib bi Jon tiingi tv ero bi Filadelfia
\p 
\v 7 “Nyon tv enjel nyi ero bi Filadelfia re,
\p “Alum nya ana, nya Mbarebara Nne Esowo no li Etingitingi Nne yahke bung, ye ji kpi egbokoro ji Devid. Á lꞌlennge, nnene limm, no bahke ma bam. Á lꞌbam, nnene limm, no bahke ma lennge.
\p 
\v 8 “N kpꞌkahne eltum ena ni a kpꞌlimi. Me n lennge mbutahk bum-a, mi nne awohng awohng lꞌkꞌma bam.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Ell 5:6\f* N kpꞌkahne re, a kpi mmonsahm ntiil. Wobbum alum enyame. A tikem gbaame re, mbing enyame, a nyimm.
\v 9 Wuungu atung! Ana ellong ane ba li ka nnehm, ba kpo lung elbo re, ‘Jus’, na nyehne, bo akimfahnge nya. M bahke limi bo, bo jo ba, ba gong kak-a, eji bo lꞌkahn re, a kp-m lohko kor.
\v 10 Tibre wobbum alum enyame nya n tong-a re, wo jo kpuumu.\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Hib 10:36\f* Owo fvfo m bahk-a tob tahre yehke go egburu elgaare ni bahke bake go njini nyia kpee, ni nne awohng awohng no li go njini nyia bahke yele.\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Ell 13:1-10\f*
\v 11 M bahke gulu elbake. Yiimi tꞌtahne go mbang nyi a kpꞌtoono, eji nne awohng awohng lꞌkꞌtaare ekpasi eltuuru eja.
\p 
\v 12 “Nne no lꞌga anebekv ebe, m bahk-e limi, á jol ana ego go etahk Esowo ebame. Á nehm tiki tahm etahk jio sa. M bahke nyono mbing nyi Esowo ebame go ege a ngubjing, fere nyon-e mbing ejahbe ji Esowo ebame, Jeusalem ji nfenfe, jio ji bahke lohngo go ejahbetul ji Esowo ebame ba.\f + \fr 3:12 \ft Ell 21:2\f* M bahk-e tob nyon mbing enyame nyi nfenfe fvfo.\f + \fr 3:12 \ft Ell 19:12\f*
\p 
\v 13 “Nne no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk ji Etingi Etohko kpꞌbungu tong aneb ero.
\s1 Etib bi Jon tiingi tv ero bi Laodisea
\p 
\v 14 “Nyon tv enjel nyi ero bi Laodisea re,
\p “Alum nya ana, nya nne no bo kpo lung-e re, ‘Emen’ yahke bung, ye ji li etingitingi ntianse nyi kpi ekakesehk. Ye wo li mbomannahb go nsol nyi Esowo limi no kpee.\f + \fr 3:14 \ft Jon 1:2; Kol 1:15\f*
\p 
\v 15 “N kpꞌkahne eltum ena ni a kpꞌlimi. A li ana alahb ma kil fubu, jol elnaange nehme naange. Kor-m re wo fub, tohko jol ano, wo naange na.
\p 
\v 16 “Eji a li ana alahb ma ma rongo na rongo, ma kil fubu, jol elnaange nehme naange, m bahk-a fahme na wohng go.
\v 17 Tibre a kpꞌbungu re, ‘Me n fang, anv, me n jol njꞌjoka nne. Ejumjum limm, ji n kpꞌkpeke seb.’\f + \fr 3:17 \ft 1 Kor 4:8\f* Na nyehne ga, a nehme kahn re, a li erem erem, fere kpꞌfili ane ndon. Wobgbo ekpak, fere wa amahr, fere kpꞌjene ebun ebun.
\v 18 Owo wahnge n kp-a tubu elle re, wo ba ga egame, ba gunu agul nya nno a nno, nya bo ma tuungu tahl go agun, eji a lꞌfang,\f + \fr 3:18 \ft 1 Pit 1:7\f* wo fere tob gunu abarebare nsol nya a bahke jo liibi, eji a lꞌkꞌkpe jen ebun ebun, fere jo riki elna ndon,\f + \fr 3:18 \ft Ell 19:8\f* wo fere tob gunu ekahm amahr, jo to go amahr, eji a lꞌnyehn.\f + \fr 3:18 \ft Luk 18:41\f*
\v 19 N kpo nyam ane ba kp-m koro, fere jo kak bo erem.\f + \fr 3:19 \ft 1 Kor 11:32; Hib 12:6\f* Niiri lꞌlun, wo yake mbang enya nyio.
\v 20 Anv, me n noa, yim go mbutahk kpꞌkahde.\f + \fr 3:20 \ft Luk 12:36\f* Nne awohng awohng no lꞌwuk ellum ename, fere lennge mbu, m bahke yele go ege ekpꞌkpa, ba li nsol a ne, ye tob li nsol a name.\fig Anv, me n noa, yim go mbutahk kpꞌkahde...|alt="Jesus standing at the door knocking" src="cn01954C.tif" size="col" loc="Ellennge 3:20" ref="3:20"\fig*\f + \fr 3:20 \ft Jon 14:23\f*
\p 
\v 21 “Nne no lꞌga anebekv ebe, m bahk-e kake nsahm nyi á bahke jehke a name go egame eti etul jang jang ana m ma ga anebekv ebame, fere song ji a Nsoo go ege eti etul.
\p 
\v 22 “Nne no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk ji Etingi Etohko kpꞌbungu tong aneb ero.”
\c 4
\s1 Eti etul ji Esowo
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm kpe tab esamahr, soro nyehn mbutahk mi ejahbetul Esowo ma lennge. Nne no n wuk-e no, no gbo mbang bung a name, ellum ene jolo ana ntang, á bungu re, “Wahr, wo ba ga ero! M bahk-a tibi nsol nyi bahke limi toono nyia.”
\p 
\v 2 Etingi Etohko kehm soro rod-m tvtv, n kehm soro nyehn eti etul go ejahbetul Esowo, fere nyehn nne jehk no.
\v 3 Nne no ji eti etul jio, á jolo go elfoongo ni atal nya nno a nno, eltal nehko bo kpo lung re ejaspa, nehko bo kpo lung re ekarnilian. Ebangenjok jolo o sennge eti etul jio kak, jolo are eltal ni nno a nno ni, ni bo kpo lung re emerald.
\p 
\v 4 Eltahl a nji etul eni jolo sennge eti etul jio kak. Eltahl anebkul ani ba ji o, ba kake abarebare nsol, fere konngo akpasi agul.
\v 5 Amangedu, alum, a aran, kpee nsol nyia jo lohngo go eti etul jio. Enyaale na ebsehma bi bo nyaale no bum, jo lul go mbuksong eti etul jio, bio bi li etohko na ebsehma bi Esowo.
\v 6 Ejum jolo ona, ji jolo ana eto ji jo foongo enyehn, fere sahb wꞌwili, are eltal ni nno a nno ni, ni bo kpo lung re ekristel. Enyam eni noongo sennge eti etul jio kak. Anyehng anyehng jo noongo go ege ejang. Bo bele amahr gbalee go ala, a njahm.
\p 
\v 7 Nnyam nyehko jolo ana egabe, nyehko jolo ana nfong, nyehko bele esamahr ana bi nne, nyehko jolo ana ebtere bi kpꞌfonngo.
\v 8 Enyam bio na eni bele akpungkpung arakera arakera. Amahr saabe na saabe bo kpee ejang ngubjing ajehng ajehng, a atahng atahng. Atv a njul, bo joom tiki rahke ase ayimi re,
\q1 “Jehova no gbale sehng,
\q1 ye wo li mbarebare, ye wo li mbarebare,
\q1 ye ji jolo go mbomannahb, á noa anv,
\q1 á bahke kpe feere ba.”
\p 
\v 9 Ngare anyehng anyehng nyi enyam bio na eni lꞌkehme ase yim, jo tehk Esowo bi jehk go eti etul jio, ye ji li go njinanjini, fere jo ka-e ellub, jo kak-e saam,
\v 10 eltahl anebkul ani bao kpo kono elgboko go alata nne no jehk go eti etul jio, jo kak-e, ye ji li go njinanjini, fere jo lennge akpasi eltuuru ebo, ro tv go mbuksong eti etul jio, fere jo bung re,
\q1 
\v 11 “Esowo Ntul ewahre, fꞌfuumu re, wo bel ellub, fere bel ekpunu, a nsahm.
\q1 Tibre wo li nne no limi nsol kpee.
\q1 Ana kor-a no wo, a limi no re jol, fere kpin.”
\c 5
\s1 Nwer nyi mmon a njoro ko no
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm nyehne nwer go eboblum bi nne no jehk go eti etul jio, nyi bo nyono njahm ebal ebal, fehd, fere lake elak edi na ebsehma, bi lohngo re bobbulu nwer.
\v 2 N nyehne njꞌjoka enjel nyi bungu wahre wahre re, “Nne awo fuumu re á laade alak nyaa, fere lennge nwer nyia?”
\p 
\v 3 Nnene jolem go ejahbetul Esowo, jol go njini nyia, jol go atahng ndi, no male lennge nwer nyio, fere nyehn atahng.
\p 
\v 4 N lingi sehng, eji nnene ki jol, no fuumu re á lennge nwer nyio, fere nyehn atahng.
\v 5 Nnenkul awohng kehm-m tongo re, “Ka kpe ling, nyehnee, egabe ji lohng go etꞌtohngo ji Juda, ye ji li nlohk nyi Devid,\f + \fr 5:5 \ft Mat 22:45\f* ebnok ebta ga anebekv ebe, á bahke ma laade alak nyao na asehma, fere lennge nwer nyio.”\f + \fr 5:5 \ft Ell 22:16\f*
\p 
\v 6 Owo n kehm nyehne mmon a njoro yim go elka ni eti etul jio. Enyam bio na eni jolo o sennge kak, a anebkul bao fvfo. Mmon a njoro noo jolo are bo m-e wul na. Á bele ntang na esehma, fere bel amahr na asehma nya li etohko na ebsehma bi Esowo tumu no tv go njini kpee.\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Ell 4:5\f*
\p 
\v 7 Mmon a njoro noo kehm tahme song taare nne no ji go eti etul jio nwer nyi á fili go eboblum.
\v 8 Eji á ma taare nwer nyio, enyam bio na eni kehm gboko go ndi go alata nya mmon a njoro noo. Eltahl anebkul ani bao tob limi ano fvfo. Nne awohng awohng fili ebuk, fere fili ekpingi ji bo limi go agul, ji bo kake alakenti nya bo kake agun, jo teebe, jo v esꞌsvv eleenge, nya li ero bi aneb Esowo kpo kak.
\v 9 Bo jo yimi ese nfenfe re,
\q1 “A fꞌfuumu re, wo ko nwer nyio, laade alak lennge, tibre bo ma-a wul, wobyake alung ema ka, gunu ane ka Esowo go nnahb anyehng anyehng, a ane ba kpo bung ajahbe nya bo ebo ebo go ejang njini abehng abehng, a ejahbe ajehng ajehng.
\v 10 Wobbob bo etul, fere lim bo jol abalimajom, eji bo lꞌjo loko Esowo. Bo ba bahke jo fili njini.”\f + \fr 5:10 \ft Ell 20:6\f*
\p 
\v 11 N kehm seenge, soro wuk babenjel. Bo jolo mbud a nkunu sennge eti etul jio kak, go enyam bio na eni, a anebkul bao fvfo.
\v 12 Bo kehm kehme elbungu wahre wahre re,
\q1 “Mmon a njoro no bo m-e wul, fuumu re á bel nsahm, fere gbo afang, bel elkahne, fere bel eko, bel ekpunu, fere bel ellub, a elfuulu.”\f + \fr 5:12 \ft Fil 2:9-10\f*
\p 
\v 13 N kehm kpe wuk ejum ajehng ajehng ji Esowo limi no go elbung abola ndi, a atahng ndi, go alahb, a nsol kpee, jo bungu re,
\q1 “Nong, elfuulu, ekpunu, ellub, a nsahm jol ka nne no jehk go eti etul jio, a mmon a njoro go njinanjini.”
\p 
\v 14 Enyam bio na eni kehm bungu re, “Emen.” Anebkul bao kehm soro gbo go ndi, kak Esowo.
\c 6
\s1 Ana mmon a njoro lennge nwer nyio
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm nyehne ana mmon a njoro noo kpꞌlaade ngbokambang elak go alak nyao na asehma. N kehm wuku ellum ni nnyam anyehng nyi woomo go ellong enyam eni bio, nyi bungu ana ndan re,
\p “Ba!”
\p 
\v 2 Owo n kehm nyehne mbarebare enyꞌnya. Nne no kuum-e go njahm, á fili elban. Bo konng-e ekpasi ntul. Á kehm lohngo tahm song nok ebta, fere ga anebekv ebe. Tibre ano wo wahnge á je no.
\p 
\v 3 Eji mmon a njoro noo kpe laade etoono elak behko bi biingi alak abal, n kehm wuku etoono nnyam nyehko nyi kpe bung re,
\p “Ba!”
\p 
\v 4 Enyꞌnya jehko kehm kpe lohng ba, ji jolo mbilibili. Nne no kuum-e go njahm, bo ka-e nsahm re, á ko ebta ba a bi go njini, eji ane lꞌjo wul atemtem. Bo ka-e ekahngkahng bi nnen a nnen.\f + \fr 6:4 \ft Mat 24:6\f*
\p 
\v 5 Eji mmon a njoro noo kpe laade etoono elak behko bi biingi alak abal, n kehm wuku etoono nnyam nyehko nyi kpe bung re,
\p “Ba!” N kehm kpe nyehn nnyakenyake enyꞌnya. Nne no kuum-e go njahm fili ejum nsol agare go ege ebo.
\v 6 N wuku ejum ana ellum ni lohngo go ellong enyam bio na eni, ni bungu re, “Nkob a nkohl, bo bahke jo gungu go nsiring era, ngbugu atehke go nsiring era. Ka rannge akehng, a alahb avain!”
\p 
\v 7 Eji mmon a njoro noo kpe laade elak behko bi biingi alak ara, n kehm kpe wuk etoono nnyam nyehko nyi kpe bung re,
\p “Ba!”
\p 
\v 8 N kehm soro nyehn mbammebamme enyꞌnya. Nne no kuum-e go njahm, mbing enye, bo jo lung-e re Elkv. Ejahbe akvne jo toon-e njahm. Bo ka bo nsahm re bo ko ekahngkahng, njal, ayam, a abibbib enyam ba wul ejang ane ba li go njini. Go ejang emni bi ane ba li go njini, ejang ajehng bahke kpoko.
\p 
\v 9 Eji mmon a njoro noo kpe laade elak behko bi biingi alak alon, n kehm nyehne edi njom alimi. Nla edi njom o, n nyehne atohko ane ba jo bung alum Esowo, ba bo wulu no tib go bo a ntianse nyi bo jo yiimi.
\v 10 Bo kehm rabe wahre wahre re, “Mbarebare Esowo bi gbale sehng, bi li go etingitingi, bahke kange renan, a kehm lame ane ba li go njini, fere bongo bo tib go elwulu ni bo wul-r no?”
\p 
\v 11 Owo bo kehm kake nne awohng awohng mbarebare ekpawobo, fere tong bo re, bo ji, re ekv mmongare ntiil, tete nfange nyi alokeltum bako ba li abonanyehn biingi, ba bo bahke tob wul bo jang jang ana bo wulu bo.
\p 
\v 12 Eji mmon a njoro noo kpe laade elak behko bi biingi alak arakera, n kehm nyehne ana ndi kpꞌsahb gbꞌgbehke.\f + \fr 6:12 \ft Mat 24:7\f* Njul kehm soro gbo ejannge, fere jol ana nnyakenyaka mbomo. Ebareka fere jol, are alung ma.
\v 13 Alonlo nya li go elbung jo fooro gbo go ndi ana akab arokpa kpo fooro gbo, eji nfeb nyi nnen kpꞌlimi.
\v 14 Elbung kehm daade ana nwer nyi bo ma fehd. Ewong ajehng ajehng kpeem jol edi ji jolo no. Ajahbe nya jolo go elka alahb kpeem jol adi nya jolo no. Bo rodo kpee yaange adi bum.\f + \fr 6:14 \ft Mat 24:29\f*
\p 
\v 15 Atul ba njini, a ajꞌjok ane, a atubesi nsoja, a afang ane, a agburu ane, a ane kpee, afi jolo aju, afi jolo ane baka baka, bo be, jo biiri go akpartal, fere jo biiri go afukatal nya li go awong,
\v 16 fere jo gboongo awong, a akpartal re, “Mehlen, bul-r, wahn behr-r, eji nne no jehk go eti etul lꞌki-r nyehn, eji erakatahng ji mmon a njoro lꞌkꞌgbo tub-r.\f + \fr 6:16 \ft Luk 23:30\f*
\v 17 Tibre egburu efung bi erakatahng ebo ebrehng. Nne awo bahke sahbe yiimi go nfem ana nyio?”\f + \fr 6:17 \ft Rom 2:5\f*
\c 7
\s1 Ana nfange nyi aneb Israel li no
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm nyehne enjel na eni yim no go nkpohka njini nyio na eni. Bo ma jabbe nfeb nyio na eni nyi li go njini, eji nfeb anyehng anyehng lꞌkꞌkpe lim go ndi, fere lim go agburu aya, fere lim eti ajehng ajehng.
\p 
\v 2 N kehm kpe nyehn enjel nyehko kpꞌlohngo go ero nfam abake. Á fili ejum ji Esowo bi li go elkpin kpo ko, kak elliingi ene. Enjel nyio kehm rabe wahre wahre lung enjel nyehko na eni nyi bo ka bo nsahm nyi bo bahke kake ndi erem, a agburu aya.
\v 3 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Kana waka kak ndi erem, a aya, a nti, tete wahr kak alokeltum ba Esowo ebahre elliingi go bo a mbuk.”
\p 
\v 4 N wuku nfange ane nyi bo kake bo elliingi. Nfange ane nyio jolo ane atahltahl nkpel atahlku, a nkpelatahl ara (144,000), nyi lohngo go etꞌtohngo ajehng ajehng ji Israel.
\v 5 Ane ba lohngo go etꞌtohngo ji Juda, ba bo kake bo elliingi, bo jolo ane atahltahl nkpel eltahl ewubu (12,000), etꞌtohngo ji Ruben, ane tob jolo ano, etꞌtohngo ji Gad, ane tob jolo ano,
\v 6 etꞌtohngo ji Aser, ane tob jolo ano, etꞌtohngo ji Naftali, ane tob jolo ano, etꞌtohngo ji Manase, ane tob jolo ano,
\v 7 etꞌtohngo ji Simeon, ane tob jolo ano, etꞌtohngo ji Livai, ane tob jolo ano, etꞌtohngo ji Isasa, ane tob jolo ano,
\v 8 etꞌtohngo ji Sebulon, ane tob jolo ano, etꞌtohngo ji Josef, ane tob jolo ano, etꞌtohngo ji Benjamin, ane tob jolo ano fvfo.
\s1 Ellong ane gbalee
\p 
\v 9 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn ellong ane tvv, ni nne awohng awohng lꞌkꞌma fange. Bo lohngo go ejahbe ajehng ajehng, go nnahb anyehng anyehng, go ejang njini abehng abehng, a ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji kpo bung eje eje. Bo yiimi go mbuksong eti etul jio, go esamahr bi mmon a njoro. Bo liibi abarebare akpawobo, fere fili amang go bo abo.
\v 10 Bo jo rabe wahre wahre re,
\q1 “Eltahre enahre lohng goji Esowo ebahre bi jehk go eti etul, a mmon a njoro.”
\p 
\v 11 Eti etul jio, a anebkul bao, a enyam bio na eni, babenjel yiimi sennge bo kpee kak. Bo kehm gboko kohk asamahr ebo go ndi go mbuksong eti etul jio, kak Esowo,
\v 12 fere jo bung re,
\q1 “Emen. Elfuulu, ellub, elkahne, ekpunu, nsahm, a eko jol ka Esowo ebahre bi e kp-e kake saam go njinanjini. Emen.”
\p 
\v 13 Nnenkul awohng kehm-m bahbe re, “Ane aba ana, ba ma liibi abarebare akpawobo? Gan wo bo lohng no ba?”
\p 
\v 14 N kehm-e faange re, “Nsoo, a kpꞌkahne.” Á kehm-m tongo re, “Ane baa ana eblohng go egburu erem bi ebnohko.\f + \fr 7:14 \ft Ell 6:9\f* Bobru akpawobo ebo go alung ma mmon a njoro ebbar.\f + \fr 7:14 \ft Hib 9:14\f*
\v 15 Ano wo wahnge bo yim go mbuksong eti etul ji Esowo, fere kp-e kake atv a njul go ege etahk, ye jio ji jehk go eti etul jio, á li a bo o, kpi bo konngo ana elbultahk.
\p 
\v 16 “Njal anyehng anyehng nehm kpe jo yam bo, jol alahb nehm kpe jo kor bo. Njul nehm kpe jo fub bo. Ewannge nehm kpe jo lim bo.
\v 17 Tibre mmon a njoro no jehk go elka eti etul bahke jolo mbꞌbaabe abo.\f + \fr 7:17 \ft Jon 10:1-16\f* Á bahke tahme a bo, song tib bo alahb ma elkpin, ma kpꞌtubu mbꞌbehl. Esowo bahke fulu bo abonngo kpee go amahr.”
\c 8
\s1 Elak bi biingi alak asehma
\p 
\v 1 Eji mmon a njoro noo laade elak behko bi biingi alak asehma, ejahbetul Esowo naange na naange kpꞌtii go ejang awa.
\p 
\v 2 Owo n kehm nyehne enjel na esehma nyi yiimi go esamahr bi Esowo. Bo ka bo ntang na esehma.
\p 
\v 3 Enjel nyehko kehm lohngo ba yiimi go edi njom alimi ji bo limi go agul, ji jolo go mbuksong eti etul ji Esowo. Á fili ekpingi agul, ji bo kpo kak alakenti nya bo jo nyaale. Bo ka-e alakenti gbalee re á kunu go edi njom alimi jio semme ero bi aneb Esowo kpee kpo kak.
\v 4 Atꞌtohk jo longo go alakenti nyao nya enjel nyio fili go ebo, fere jo tahm go ero, song rehng esamahr bi Esowo, semme aro nya aneb Esowo.
\p 
\v 5 Owo enjel nyio kehm koko ekpingi ji alakenti kpo woomo, kehm song kpar agun go edi njom alimi kak, rur go ekpingi jio, kehm sale wohng go njini. Owo aran kehm kehme eltake, edi jo wahl, amangedu jo lim, ndi jo gbehke.
\s1 Ntang na esehma
\p 
\v 6 Owo enjel nyio na esehma nyi bele ntang na esehma kehm toobo ebjing bi bo bahke woro atang nyao.
\p 
\v 7 Ngbokambang enjel kehm woro ntang enye. Elahb atal ji jolo semme alung, a agun kehm kehm elnake. Ejang njini ajehng ji fi no, sa ejang ebbal. Go ejang ebra bi nti nyi li go njini, ejang ajehng ji fi. Ajele nya mbir mbir fi kpee.
\p 
\v 8 Etoono enjel kehm tob wor ntang enye. Bo kehm rodo ejum ji jolo go elfoongo ni egburu ewong ji jo lul, tub kak go agburu aya.
\v 9 Go ejang ebra bi aya kpee ma li go njini, ejang ajehng ji siingi alung. Go ejang ebra bi enyam alahb kpee bi li go njini, ejang ajehng ji kpo. Go ejang ebra bi agbang kpee nya li go njini, ejang ajehng ji rannge.
\p 
\v 10 Etoono enjel nyi biingi enjel era kehm woro ntang enye. Egburu elonlo ji jo lul ana enyaale kehm fooro go elbung, ba gbo yel go ngba, a aya aya, a adi nya alahb kpo lohng.
\v 11 Mbing elonlo nyio, bo kpo lung-e re Mbumti. Go ejang ebra bi alahb kpee ma li go njini, ejang ajehng ji jo lul suud. Ane gbalee ba kpo no tib alahb mao, tib eji jo lul suud.
\p 
\v 12 Enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel eni kehm woro ntang enye. Bo kehm rumu njul, fere tob rum ebareka, a alonlo. Bo tele ejang ajehng gbo ejannge. Go ejang ebra bi elyake kpee ni njul, ebareka, a alonlo jo ya, ejang ajehng ji gbo ejannge. Go ejang ebra bi limi efung kohro kohro, ejang ajehng ji gbo ejannge. Go ejang ebra bi limi efung kohro kohro, ejang ajehng ji gbo ejannge. Go ejang ebra bi limi atv, ejang ajehng ji gbo ejannge.\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Mat 24:29\f*
\p 
\v 13 N kehm seenge, soro wuk ebtere kpꞌfonngo go atahng ejahbetul Esowo, fere jo bung wahre wahre re, “Eyuu, eyuu, eyuu! Erem bi nnen yahke gbo tub ane ba lene go njini tib go atang nya enjel nyehko na era yahke wor.”\f + \fr 8:13 \ft Mat 24:6\f*
\c 9
\nb 
\v 1 Enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel elon kehm woro ntang enye. N kehm nyehne elonlo ma lohng go elbung ba gbo ndi. Ye wo, bo ka-e egbokoro ji nrabbe elbing nio.
\v 2 Á kehm lennge nrabbe elbing nio o, atꞌtohk kehm lohngo, fere jo tꞌtehm ana atꞌtohk nya egburu erehm agun. Njul fere nyak na nyak, a elbung fvfo tib go atꞌtohk nya jo lohng go nrabbe elbing nio.
\v 3 Agohrobi kehm lohngo go atꞌtohk nyao, ba go njini. Bo ka bo nsahm ana nyio nyi enang.
\v 4 Bo tongo bo re, bo kꞌrannge ajele, kꞌrannge elrahnti anehng anehng, kꞌrannge eti ajehng ajehng, sehngem ane ba ki kpi elliingi ni Esowo go bo a mbuk ba ba, bo bahke rannge bo.
\v 5 Bo taamem re agohrobi nyao wul ane, sehngem ebnohko bi bi bo jo nohk bo go nnyahng elon. Ebnohko bi agohrobi nyao jo nohk ane, jolo ana nnang kpo ta nne.
\v 6 Ngare nyio o ane bahke jo seb mbang ana nyi bo bahke gulu elkpoko, jol na. Bo bahke jo seb re bo kpo. Elkv bahke tene bo.\f + \fr 9:6 \ft Luk 23:30\f*
\p 
\v 7 Agohrobi nyao jolo go elfoongo ni anyꞌnya nya bo ma toobo bo bum re bo ko bo tahm ebta. Nsol nyi bo konngo no jolo ana akpasi atul nya bo limi go agul. Asamahr ebo jolo ana asamahr ane.
\v 8 Alv esi ebo jolo ana alv esi anebkal. Amahn ebo jolo ana amahn agabe.
\v 9 Nsol nyi jolo go bo a ngang jolo ana agbanggbang nya bo limi go akuungu. Ewahl ji akpungkpung ebo jo wahl, jolo ana ewahl atꞌrok gbalee nya anyꞌnya kpꞌtohng tahm ebta.
\v 10 Bo kpi asil ana nya enang, fere bel atakelehk. Go bo asil wo, nsahm wob no, nyi bo kpo ta ane, sum bo, tete rehng nnyahng elon.
\p 
\v 11 Bo kpi ntul no kpo fili bo, ye ji li enjel nyi nrabbe elbing nio. Mbing enye go alum Hibru, bo kpo lung-e re Abadon. Go alum Grik, bo kpo lung-e re Apollion (ji lohngo re Nrꞌrannge).
\p 
\v 12 Ngbokambang erem ebsehng. Ebsa na ebal nya bahke kpe ba.
\p 
\v 13 Enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel erakera kehm woro ntang enye. N kehm wuku nne no bungu go ngoongo nyio na eni nyi edi njom alimi ji bo limi go agul, ji jolo go mbuksong Esowo.
\v 14 Á bungu tong enjel nyio nyi biingi enjel erakera nyi fili ntang re, “Fannge enjel nyio na eni nyi bo gba bo alehke bum go nkpe aya ma bo kpo lung re Yufrat, ma li aya ma nnen.”
\p 
\v 15 Owo á kehm fannge enjel nyio na eni alehke yake, ba bo toobo bo bum re bo wul ejang ane ba li go njini, elya nio lꞌrehng, nnyahng mio lꞌrehng, efung bio lꞌrehng, awa nyao lꞌrehng. Go ejang ebra bi ane ba li go njini, bo bahke wulu ejang ajehng.
\v 16 N wuku nfanga nsoja nyi kuumu go anyꞌnya. Jolo ane atahl nku a nku. (200,000,000)
\p 
\v 17 Go egame enyehnamahr, n nyehne anyꞌnya nyao. Ane ba kuumu go anyꞌnya nyao, bo lake agbanggbang nya bo limi go akuungu go bo a ngang. Agbanggbang nyao jolo ana agun fere jol ana elbung ni li saang, fere jol ana elgok. Asi anyꞌnya nyao jolo, are asi agabe nya. Agun, atꞌtohk, a asalfa jo lohngo go bo anyo.
\v 18 Go ejang ebra bi ane ba li go njini, ejang ajehng ji kpo no go arem nyao na ara. Arem nyao jolo agun, atꞌtohk, a asalfa nya jo lohng go bo anyo.
\v 19 Tibre nsahm nyi anyꞌnya nyao wob go bo anyo, a nsil ebo. Nsil ebo li ana asi enyo nya bo kpo ko tokko ane.
\p 
\v 20 Erik ane bako ba ki kpo go arem nyao, bo tikem sennge njahm go nsol nyi bo limi go bo abo. Bo tikem yake abi atohko akake, a eblom bi bo limi go agul, a asilva, a akuungu, a atal, go nti, bi kil ma nyehn, bi kil ma wuk, bi kil ma jen,\f + \fr 9:20 \ft 1 Kor 10:20\f*
\v 21 jol bo tikem rahke ane awulu, a ntaane alimi, a ejv avohko, go enoongo a ane.
\c 10
\s1 Enjel nyi fili mmonwer go ebo
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn enjel nyehko nyi nnen kpꞌbadde go ejahbetul Esowo abake. Á liibi ekparesemsem. Ebangenjok kuumu go ege esi. Esamahr ebe jolo ana njul. Akpade enye jolo ana akehrenkv nti nya jo lul.
\v 2 Á fili mmonwer go ebo, no bo ma lennge. Á rodo ekpade eboblum eje kunu go agburu aya, ekpade ebobkal, á bum go egbuk.
\v 3 Á kehm rabe wahre wahre wahre, are egabe ji. Á rabe kan ano me, aran na asehma kehm take.
\p 
\v 4 Eji aran nyao na asehma ma ta, n tahme re me n nyon. N kehm wuku ellum go ejahbetul ni bungu re, “Nsol nyi aran nyao na asehma bungu no, yab bum go, ka nyon!”
\p 
\v 5 Enjel nyio nyi n nyehn-e no, nyi kunu ekpade jehko go alahb, fere bum ekpade jehko go egbuk, kehm tabe eboblum ebe ton go elbung,
\v 6 fere nyam enyam go mbing nyi Esowo bi li go njinanjini, ye ji limi elbung, a nsol kpee nyi li go elbung, fere lim njini, a nsol kpee nyi li go njini, fere lim alahb, a nsol kpee nyi wob go alahb. Enjel nyio bungu re, “Esowo nehm kpe laange nkpel anyehng anyehng.
\v 7 Ngare nyio nyi enjel nyi biingi enjel na esehma yahke wor ntang enye,\f + \fr 10:7 \ft 1 Kor 15:52\f* owo ntoobo nyi Esowo toobo no go ege eltim, tong alokeltum ebe ba li abanyehnamahr bahke kehm limi mal.”\f + \fr 10:7 \ft Elt 3:21; 1 Tes 4:16-17\f*
\p 
\v 8 Ellum ni n wuku go ejahbetul Esowo ni jo bung a name, kehm kpe bung a name re, “Song, wo song ko nwer nyio nyi ma lennge, nyi enjel fili go ebo, ye ji yim, kunu ekpade jehko go alahb, fere bum ekpade jehko go egbuk.”
\p 
\v 9 N kehm jeke goji enjel nyio, song tong-e re, á ka-m mmonwer noo. Á kehm-m tongo re, “Ko, wo li! Bahk-a jo liiki go nnyo ana akehng ekon, fere jo gell-a ala.”
\p 
\v 10 N kehm taare enjel nyio mmonwer noo no á fili go ebo li. Jo liik-m go egama nnyo, are akehng ekon ma. Eji m ma li mal, kehm-m kehme ala gelle.
\p 
\v 11 Bo kehm-m tongo re, “A bahke kpe nyehn amahr nya Esowo bade ane gbalee, a ajahbe tvv, a ane ba kpo bung ajahbe ebo nya li nkohn a nkohn, a atul gbalee.”
\c 11
\s1 Atianse na abal
\p 
\v 1 Owo bo kehm-m kake ejum ana ejiingi ji bo kpo ko gare nsol, fere tong-m re, “Song, wo song gare etahk Esowo, wo tob gare edi njom alimi, a ane ba kpo kak Esowo o.
\v 2 Ka gare nlaaga etahk Esowo! Yake na yake! Tibre bobyake ka ane baka baka ba ki li Jus. Bo bahke jo jade mbarebare ejahbe jio go bo akpade go nnyahng atahl abal a nnyahng ebal.
\v 3 M bahke kake atianse enyame na abal nya bahke jo kak agbajake nsol nsahm nyi bo bahke jo nyehn amahr tete nfung atahltahl nkpel era a nfung atahl ara nyio mal (1,260).”
\p 
\v 4 Atianse nyao na abal nya li nti ebal nyio nyi bo kpo lung re oliv, nyi yim go esamahr bi Jehova bi li Ntul a njini. Bo jꞌnehm o ba li etꞌrekahng ebbal bi jehk go esamahr Esowo.
\v 5 Nnekv awohng awohng no lꞌgare re á lim bo ejum, agun bahke lohngo go bo anyo fi-e. Ano wo fvfo, nne awohng awohng no lꞌgare re á lim bo ejum, bo bahk-e wulu.
\v 6 Bo bahke bele nsahm nyi bo bahke ma sahde elahb go elnake ngare nyi bo kpꞌnyehne amahr nya Esowo, fere bel nsahm nyi bo bahke ma lim alahb siingi alung, fere kak njini erem abehng abehng ngare anyehng anyehng nyi koro bo.
\p 
\v 7 Ngare nyi bo ma yiimi ntianse nyi Esowo mal, owo ebibbib nnyam nyi bahke lohngo go nrabbe elbing nio bahke noko ebta a bo, ga bo, fere wul bo.\f + \fr 11:7 \ft Ell 13:1,7\f*
\v 8 Akv ebo bahke noongo go elatahkgur egburu ejahbe ji bo kumu Ntul abo go ekros.\f + \fr 11:8 \ft Luk 13:34\f* Esowo ebfaake mbing nyi Sodom, go Ijib gungu ejahbe jio.
\v 9 Nfung era kunu esi nyi ane bahke jo nyehn akv nyao. Bo bahke lohngo go ajoobo ajahbe tvv ba, a adi nkohn a nkohn, a ajang njini gbalee fvfo. Bo bahke jo bung ajahbe ebo, nya li nkohn a nkohn. Bo nehm taame re, bo kpa bo kak.
\v 10 Ane ba li go njini, eltim bahke bo yebe sehng tib go elkv ni ane abal bao ma kpo. Bo bahke limi elkak, fere jo yare atem, tibre abanyehnamahr bao na abal ko erem gbalee ba kak ane ba li go njini.
\p 
\v 11 Eji ma kang nfung nyio na era kunu esi, owo etohko ji kpo ka elkpin kehm lohngo goji Esowo, ba yel bo. Bo kehm soro tahm yiimi. Ane kpee ba jo nyehn bo, kehm kehme elfahle tete.
\v 12 Owo bo kehm wuku ellum go ejahbetul Esowo ni bungu wahre wahre re, “Wahren, ba ga ero!” Eji anebekv ebo kpi bo seenge, ekparesemsem kehm rodo bo tahm a bo go ejahbetul Esowo.
\v 13 Ngare nyꞌnehm ona ndi kehm kehme elgbehke tete. Go ejang ebwubu bi ejahbe jio, ejang ajehng ji wa no. Ane jolo atahltahl nkpel atahl anehkeni a nkpel elku (7,000) ba kpo no tib go ndi agbehke nyio. Erik ane bako ba sa no, anyar lamme bo sehng. Bo kehm kehme Esowo bi li go ero ellub ka.
\p 
\v 14 Etoono erem bi biingi arem abal ebmal. Etoono erem behko bi yahke kpe ba.
\s1 Ntang nyi biingi ntang esehma
\p 
\v 15 Etoono enjel nyi biingi enjel esehma kehm woro ntang enye. Owo ane ba li go ejahbetul Esowo kehm bungu wahre wahre re, “Esowo bi li Ntul ewahre, a Mesaya enye, bobfere ko etul bi njini nyia. Esowo bahke fili njini ano ano go njinanjini.”
\p 
\v 16 Eltahl anebkul ani ba ji go nti etul ebo go esamahr Esowo, kehm gboko kohk asamahr ndi, kak Esowo,
\v 17 fere bung re,
\q1 “E ma-a kak saam Jehova no gbal sehng, wo ji li anv, wo ji jolo mahne mahne, tibre wobko egburu nsahm enya, fere kehme njini fili.
\q1 
\v 18 Aneb njini, atahng jo rake bo tete. Tibre ngare erakatahng enya ebbiingi, nyi a bahke lame akvne.
\q1 Ngare nyio nyi a bahke tuuru alokeltum eba, fere tuuru abanyehnamahr eba, a abarebare ane eba, a nne awohng awohng no kpo fahl mbing enya, afi á jolo ntul, afi á jolo nja.
\q1 Ngare ebbingi nyi a bahke rannge ane ba rannge njini nyia.”
\p 
\v 19 Owo bo kehm lennge mbutahk mi etahk Esowo ji li go ejahbetul eje. Bo kehm nyehne elkohl ni egbanngalung ji Esowo limi a ane ebe, jehk go etahk Esowo. Amangedu jo limi ona, a ewahl ane. Aran kehm kehme eltake na ta, ndi fere jo gbehke, elahb atal kehm kehme elnake.
\c 12
\s1 Nnenkal, a edꞌragon
\p 
\v 1 Egburu elliingi kehm tibi go ejahbetul Esowo. Jolo nnenkal no ma liibi njul go ngubjing, fere kunu akpade go ebareka. Á konngo ekpasi ntul ji bele ewubu elonlo na ebbal.
\v 2 Ngare nyio á jolo ela. Á kehm rabe eling tib go elyame ni jo yam-e, eji á yahke jel mmon.
\p 
\v 3 Elliingi nehko kehm kpe tib go ejahbetul Esowo. Jolo egburu edꞌragon ji bili bil, ji bele esi na ebsehma, a ntang na ewubu. Á konngo ekpasi ntul go esi ajehng ajehng.
\v 4 Go ejang ebra bi alonlo kpee nya li go elbung, edꞌragon jio kehm feenge ejang ajehng go ege elsil wohng go njini. Á kehm yiimi nnenkal no yahke jel go esamahr, eji á lꞌmele mmon noo, á lꞌsi jel-e jel.
\v 5 Nnenkal noo kehm jele nnenlum, no bahke njini kpee fili go ebti bi bo limi go ekuungu.\f + \fr 12:5 \ft Ell 2:27; 19:15\f* Bo kehm soro ba gbiiri mmon noo, tahm a ne goji Esowo, a eti etul eje.
\v 6 Nnenkal noo kehm soro be tahm go elka emahng, edi jio ji Esowo toobo bum-e, eji á lꞌle-e nfung atahltahl nkpel era a nfung atahl ara nyio (1,260).\f + \fr 12:6 \ft Ell 11:2\f*
\p 
\v 7 Ebta kehm gboko go ejahbetul Esowo. Maikel, a enjel enye, bo kehm kehme elnoko a edꞌragon jio. Edꞌragon, a enjel enye kehm tob kehme elnoko a bo fvfo.
\v 8 Maikel, a enjel enye kehm noko, fere ga bo.\f + \fr 12:8 \ft Jud 9\f* Edꞌragon, a enjel enye, edi ajehng ajehng kpeem jol go ejahbetul Esowo ka bo.
\v 9 Bo kehm kame egburu edꞌragon jio yake go, ye ji li nkꞌkula nnyo nyi bo kpo lung-e re nnehm, fere jo lung-e re Nnekv,\f + \fr 12:9 \ft Mat 13:28\f* ye ji ma nehm njini nyia kpee. Ye wo, bo rod-e no tub go ndi, a enjel enye.
\p 
\v 10 N kehm wuku ellum go ejahbetul Esowo ni jo bung wahre wahre re,
\q1 “Anv, eltahre ebba. Esowo ebahre ebtib nsahm enye. Etul ebe ebba.
\q1 Anv, Mesaya enye nyi ma kehme edi fili. Tibre nne no jo bung ebi bade abonane ejahre, bo m-e rod tub go njini, ye jio ji jo ka bo ebi go esamahr Esowo ebahre atv a njul.\f + \fr 12:10 \ft Luk 22:31\f*
\q1 
\v 11 Bo m-e ga go ebta tib go alung ma mmon a njoro, a atianse ebo nya bo jo yiimi. Tibre elkpin ebo joom kor bo, owo wahnge bo jo taame elkv.
\q1 
\v 12 Siiken, wahn aneb ejahbetul, wahn kpee ji lene o. Eyuu a nahne, ndi abola agburu aya. Tibre yebbadde ba go egahne, a egburu erakatahng. Á kpꞌkahne re, afung enye ebsa kahbe kahbe.”
\p 
\v 13 Eji edꞌragon jio sebe no kahn re, bo m-e rod tub go ndi, á kehm kehme nnenkal no jele mmon no nlum kam.
\v 14 Nnenkal noo, bo ka-e akpungkpung na abal nya egburu ebtere, eji á lꞌbe nnyo nyio, fonngo song rehng go elka emahng, edi jio ji bo bum-e no, jo le-e go nnya era kunu esi.
\v 15 Nnyo nyio kehm kehme alahb yaange go ege a nnyo. Alahb mao kehm jo fab ana aya, jo toono nnenkal noo, eji lꞌkpu-e, tahm a ne.
\v 16 Ndi kehm kake nnenkal noo ebo, lennge nnyo eme, fere wo alahb mao ma yaange go nnyo edꞌragon jio kpee.
\v 17 Owo edꞌragon, atahng kehm-e rake tob nnenkal noo gbalee. Á kehm tahme re á song nok ebta a erik abon ebe bako kpee, bo ji kpo bum atahm nya Esowo, fere jo yiimi ntianse ka Jisos.
\v 18 Edꞌragon jio yiimi go erikehndi ji li go egbuk agburu aya.
\c 13
\s1 Abibbib enyam na ebal
\p 
\v 1 N kehm nyehne ebibbib nnyam kpꞌlohngo go agburu aya. Á bele esi na ebsehma, fere bel ntang ewubu. Á konngo ekpasi ntul go ntang anyehng anyehng. Esi ajehng ajehng eje bo nyon-e mbing a nkuk.
\v 2 Nnyam nyi n nyehne no jolo ana ngbe. Akpade enye jolo ana nya ebea. Nnyo eme jolo ana mi egabe. Edꞌragon jio kehm-e kake eko eje, fere ka-e eti etul eje, fere ka-e nsahm enye.
\v 3 Esi ajehng ji nnyam nyio jolo are bo bom-e elok elkv. Elok jio ona kehm kpoko. Njini kpee kpo bo esi area, bo kehm kehme eltoono ebi nnyam nyio.\f + \fr 13:3 \ft Ell 17:8\f*
\p 
\v 4 Ane kpee fere jo kak edꞌragon jio, tibre ye wo ka nnyam nyio nsahm enye. Bo jo kake nnyam nyio, fere jo bung re, “Nne awo li ana nnyam nyia? Nne awo bahke ma nok ebta a ne?”
\v 5 Nnyam nyio, bo ka-e nnyo mi á jo bung abi alum bade Esowo, fere jo bung nnyo. Bo ka-e nsahm re á fili edi go nnyahng atahl abal a nnyahng ebal.\f + \fr 13:5 \ft Ell 11:2\f*
\p 
\v 6 Á kehm kehme Esowo su, fere jo su mbing enye, a etahk eje. Á jo tꞌtob su ane ba lene go ejahbetul Esowo.\f + \fr 13:6 \ft Mat 24:15\f*
\v 7 Bo tꞌtaame re á nok ebta a aneb Esowo, fere ga bo. Bo ka-e nsahm re á fili nnahb anyehng anyehng, a nne awohng awohng, a ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji kpo bung eje eje.
\v 8 Nne awohng awohng no li go njini nyia bahk-e kake, no bo ki nyon mbing enye go nwer nyi elkpin, njini nyia kehm jolo. Nwer nyio li ka mmon a njoro no bo wul-e no.
\p 
\v 9 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbel atung, nong, á wuk.
\p 
\v 10 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌwahng re ntem je ngbekobo, á bahke tob je ngbekobo fvfo. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌwul nne go ntahme, go ntahme wo fvfo, bo bahke tob wul-e.\f + \fr 13:10 \ft Mat 26:52\f* Ana wo li erehke ji Esowo rehke ane ebe re bo jo kpuumu, fere jo bel ekakesehk.
\p 
\v 11 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn ebibbib nnyam nyehko kpꞌlohngo go ndi.\f + \fr 13:11 \ft 1 Jon 4:5\f* Á bele ntang ebal ana nyi mmon a njoro. Á jo bungu, are edꞌragon ji.\f + \fr 13:11 \ft Mat 7:15\f*
\v 12 Á jo fili edi go esamahr ngbokambang a nnyam nyi ka-e nsahm. Owo wahnge á jo lim re, nne awohng awohng no li go njini jo kak ngbokambang a nnyam nyi bele egburu elok ji jolo elok elkv, ma fere kpo.
\v 13 Etoono nnyam nyio limi agburu akpokosi, á jo limi agun lohng go elbung ba gbo go ndi go esamahr ane.\f + \fr 13:13 \ft Mat 24:24; 2 Tes 2:9-10\f*
\v 14 Akpokosi nya bo ka-e no re á jo lim go esamahr ngbokambang a nnyam, nya nya wahnge á jo nehm ane kpee ba li go njini, fere tong bo re bo lim elokelom go elfoongo ni ngbokambang a nnyam nyi bo bom-e elok elkv, á kpeke li go elkpin.
\v 15 Etoono nnyam nyio bele nsahm nyi á bahke ma ka elokelom jio elkpin, jio ji jolo go elfoongo ni ngbokambang a nnyam, eji elokelom jio lꞌjo bung, fere jo wul ane ba kil-e elkake.
\p 
\v 16 Etoono nnyam nyio nyi limi re nne awohng awohng bel elliingi go ege eboblum, tohko jol ano go ege a mbuk, afi nne noo jolo ntul, afi á jolo nja, afi á jolo efange nne, afi á jolo nkpak, afi á jolo nju, afi nju á jolem.
\v 17 Nne awohng awohng joom ma gunu, fere gꞌgungu, sehngem re no, á bele elliingi nio ni li mbing nyi nnyam nyio, tohko jol ano, nfange nyi yim go mbing nyio.
\v 18 Nsol nyia nyi Esowo kp-r rehke re, wahr bel elkahne. Ye ji kpi elkahne, nong, á gabe ana nfange a nnyam nyio lohngo no. Tibre nfange nyio, nyi nne nyi, li atahltahl atahl awubu atahl ara kunu nsol erakera (666).
\c 14
\s1 Ana aneb Esowo yiimi go ewong ji bo kpo lung re Sayon
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm seenge, soro nyehn mmon a njoro yim no go ewong ji bo kpo lung re Sayon. Ane ba jolo a ne o, ba bo nyono mbing a mmon a njoro, a mbing a Nde go bo a mbuk. Bo jolo ane atahltahl nkpel atahlku, a nkpel atahl ara (144,000).\f + \fr 14:1 \ft Ell 7:4\f*
\v 2 N kehm wuku ewahl ji lohng go ejahbetul Esowo, ji jolo ana elahb ji nnen a nnen, fere wuk ana aran kpꞌtake. Ewahl ji n wuku no jolo ana ewahl ane ba kpꞌkubu abuk.
\v 3 Bo yiimi go esamahr eti etul jio, a esamahr enyam bio na eni, a esamahr anebkul bao, jo yim ese ji nfenfe ji nne awohng awohng lꞌkꞌma kpili, sehngem ellong ane ba jolo ane atahltahl nkpel atahlku, a nkpel atahl ara (144,000), ba bo ma fak bo go njini nyia yake, bo ba bahke ma kpili.
\p 
\v 4 Ane bao ba li ane ba ki noongo a anebkal, tib eji bo li agol.\f + \fr 14:4 \ft 2 Kor 11:2; Ef 5:27\f* Bo kpo toono mmon a njoro edi ajehng ajehng ji á lꞌje. Bo ba li agbokombang ane ba bo ma fak bo yake go ellong ane kpee ba li njini, ka Esowo, a mmon a njoro.
\v 5 Nnene tikem wuk efahnge ajehng ajehng go bo anyo. Tibre ebꞌbi ajehng ajehng go bo atahng wobem.
\s1 Enjel na era
\p 
\v 6 N kehm nyehne enjel nyehko kpꞌfonngo go elka ejahbetul Esowo. Á bele nnoobo etib bi li go njinanjini, bi á bahke tiingi ane ba li go njini, go ejahbe ajehng ajehng, a nnahb anyehng anyehng, a nne awohng awohng, go ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji kpo bung eje eje.
\v 7 Owo á kehm bungu wahre wahre re, “Jo fahlen Esowo, wahn jo ka-e ellub. Tibre ngare ebrehng nyi á bahke lame njini. Jo kaken ye ji limi elbung, a ndi, fere lim agburu aya, a adi nya alahb kpo lohng.”
\p 
\v 8 Etoono enjel nyehko nyi lohngo toono ngbokambang, kehm bungu re, “Bebilon ebgbo! Njꞌjoka Bebilon ebgbo, ye ji ka ane kpee ba ki nyi Esowo amahm eme ma asꞌsa re bo wo.”
\p 
\v 9 Enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel era kehm kpe lohng toono enjel nyehko, kehm bungu wahre wahre re, “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌkak nnyam nyio, a elokelom jio, fere bel elliingi ene go ege a mbuk, afi jolo go ege ebo,
\v 10 á bahke tob wo amahm mao ma erakatahng ji Esowo, ma á ma yaange kak go nkob nyi erakatahng eje, ma bo ki semme ejum ajehng ajehng.\f + \fr 14:10 \ft Ell 16:19\f* Bo bahk-e nohko go agun, a asalfa go esamahr bi abarebare enjel, a bi mmon a njoro.\f + \fr 14:10 \ft Ell 19:20\f*
\v 11 Atꞌtohk agun nya bahke jo kak bo erem, bahke jo lohng go njinanjini. Ane ba jo kak nnyam nyio, fere jo kak elokelom jio nehm bel erekekv ajehng ajehng atv a njul, a nne awohng awohng no bele elliingi ni mbing enye.”\f + \fr 14:11 \ft Ell 19:3\f*
\p 
\v 12 Erehke jia li ka aneb Esowo re bo bel elkpuumu, bo jio ji kpo bum atahm nya Esowo, fere taame tv Jisos.
\p 
\v 13 N kehm wuku ellum ni bungu go ejahbetul Esowo re, “Nyon nsol nyia re, Bomo anv asongo, elfuulu li ka ane ba bahke kpoko eji bo kpꞌtoono Jehova.” Etingi Etohko kehm taame re, “Ano wo. Bo bahke reke ekv go bo a ntum, fere bel eltuuru ebo.”\f + \fr 14:13 \ft Hib 4:10\f*
\s1 Ana bo banne nkohl, fere kiimi atasok avain
\p 
\v 14 N kehm tabe esamahr, soro nyehn mbarebare ekparesemsem. Nne no ji go ekparesemsem jio, á jolo go elfoongo ni Mmon no nne. Á konngo ekpasi ntul ji bo limi go agul, fere fili ekongkong ntahme go ebo.
\p 
\v 15 Enjel nyehko kehm lohngo go etahk Esowo ba, kehm ba rabe tong nne no ji go ekparesemsem re, “Ko ntahme enya, wo ja nkohl, fere jo banne. Tibre ngare ebbiingi nyi nkohl abanne, eji nkohl nyi njini nyi ma bil.”\f + \fr 14:15 \ft Mat 13:37-43\f*
\p 
\v 16 Owo nne no ji go ekparesemsem kehm fohko ntahme enye tv go njini, ja nkohl kpee nyi li go njini, fere banne.
\p 
\v 17 Enjel nyehko kehm kpe lohng go etahk Esowo ji li go ejahbetul Esowo, ye fvfo tob fili ekongkong ntahme.
\p 
\v 18 Enjel nyehko kehm kpe lohng go edi njom alimi ji Esowo ba. Ye wo li nne no agun wob-e go ebo. Á kehm rabe wahre wahre tong nne no fili ekongkong ntahme re, “Ko ntahme enya, wo kiimi atasok avain nya li go njini kpee, tibre akab enye ebbil.”
\p 
\v 19 Enjel nyio kehm fohko ntahme enye tv go njini, kiimi atasok avain nyao kpee, soro kpu, song tuubu kak go elbing ni Esowo kpo kaame akab nti go ege erakatahng.\f + \fr 14:19 \ft Mak 12:9; Mat 24:16-21\f*
\v 20 Elbing ni bo kpo kaame akab nti jolo go esi mbang. Alung ma jo lohng go elbing nio ni bo kpo kaame akab nti kehm yele, are nnyel nyi. Nnyel alung nyio yele rehng mmal atahl awubu. Elrahbe ni rahbe no, enyꞌnya lꞌyel, bahk-e rehnge go nnyo.
\c 15
\s1 Enjel nyi gohro ko erem ba a bi
\p 
\v 1 N kehm kpe nyehn egburu elliingi go ejahbetul Esowo ni kpo-m esi sꞌsehng. Jolo enjel na esehma nyi ko arem na asehma ba a nya, nya li esꞌkohro erem. Tibre nyao kpee lꞌlim, erakatahng ji Esowo bahke male.\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Rom 1:18\f*
\v 2 N nyehne ejum ji jo foongo eto ji li anyehn anyehn,\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Ell 4:6\f* ji bo semme agun, fere nyehn ane bao ba ma ga ebi nnyam nyio, fere ga elokelom eje, fere tob ga nfange nyi mbing enye. Bo ba yiimi go nkpe eto nyio. Bo fili abuk go abo, nya Esowo ka bo.
\v 3 Bo yimi ese ji Moses ji nlokeltum Esowo, fere yim ese ji mmon a njoro re,
\q1 “Jehova no gbale sehng, nsol nyi a ma lim ebgbal, fere kpꞌkpo esi.
\q1 Ntul no njini kpee, mbang nyi a kpo lim nsol enya kpꞌnobo, li go etingitingi.
\q1 
\v 4 Ntul, nne awo lꞌki-a fahl? Nne awo lꞌkꞌka mbing enya ellub?
\q1 Tibre wo ntahngtahng wo li mbarebara nne. Njini kpee bahke ba kak wo.
\q1 Tibre atingitingi alam nya a lame no, ane kpee ebnyehn.”
\p 
\v 5 Owo n kehm kpe seenge, kehm soro nyehn edi ji sahb bꞌbar go ebkpatahk bi Esowo jo song kpiri ane ebe ma lennge.
\p 
\v 6 Enjel nyio na esehma nyi ko arem nyao na asehma ba a nya, bo lohngo o edi jio ji sahb bꞌbar. Bo kake abarebare akpawobo nya jo bar kparaang, fere gbaange agbaange nya bo limi go agul go bo akꞌkv.
\p 
\v 7 Nnyam anyehng nyi woomo go ellong enyam bio na eni kehm kake enjel nyio na esehma nkpingi na esehma bi bo limi go agul. Erakatahng ji Esowo bi li go njinanjini ruru go nkpingi nyio.
\v 8 Edi jio ji sahb bꞌbar kehm jolo atꞌtohk atꞌtohk nya lohngo goji ellub ni Esowo, a nsahm enye. Nnene kpeem jol, no kpe ma yel ekpꞌkpa jio tete arem asehma nya enjel nyio na esehma ko no ba mal.
\c 16
\s1 Nkpingi na esehma nyi erakatahng ji Esowo
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm wuku ellum ni jo bung wahre wahre go etahk Esowo tong enjel nyio na esehma re, “Songen, wahn song rod nkpingi esehma bi erakatahng ji Esowo wob no, song sale wohngo go njini.”
\p 
\v 2 Owo ngbokambang enjel kehm tahme, song rod ekpingi eje ji erakatahng ji Esowo woomo no, sale wohngo go njini. Ane ba bele elliingi ni nnyam nyio, fere jo kak elokelom eje, kehm gboko alok nya jo sahb sꞌsab, fere jo yꞌyam.
\p 
\v 3 Etoono enjel nyehko kehm rodo ekpingi eje, sale erakatahng ji Esowo kak go agburu aya. Alahb mao fere jol are alung akvne ma. Nnyam anehng anyehng nyi woomo go agburu aya kpo.
\p 
\v 4 Etoono enjel nyi biingi enjel era kehm tob yaange erakatahng ji Esowo ji woomo go ege ekpingi kak go aya, fere kak go ngba alahb, a edi ajehng ajehng ji alahb kpo lohng. Alahb mao kehm siingi alung.
\v 5 N kehm wuku enjel nyi alahb wob-e go ebo kpꞌbungu re, “Mbarebare Esowo, wo ji kpeke li anv, wo ji jolo wuku wuku, a kpo lam elam eja nob nob.
\v 6 Alung aneb Esowo ba bo wulu no, a ma abanyehnamahr Esowo fvfo ebkuumu bo. Owo wahnge a ma ka bo alung re bo wo, ana eltuuru ebo.”\f + \fr 16:6 \ft Mat 27:25\f*
\p 
\v 7 N kehm kpe wuk ellum ni bungu go edi njom alimi re, “Jehova no gbale sehng, elam eja ji a kpo lam, lohko li nob nob go etingitingi.”\f + \fr 16:7 \ft Mat 7:2; Jon 5:30\f*
\p 
\v 8 Etoono enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel eni kehm yaange erakatahng ji Esowo ji woomo go ege ekpingi wohngo go njul. Bo ka-e nsahm nyi á bahke jo fi ane go agun.
\v 9 Elfubu ni jo fub ane, jo sabe sehng. Ane kehm kehme mbing Esowo su, Esowo bi erem bio woom-e go ebo. Bo tikem gbo ndon go bo abiafem, fere jo ka-e ellub.
\p 
\v 10 Enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel elon kehm yaange erakatahng ji Esowo ji woomo go ege ekpingi wohngo go eti etul ji nnyam nyio. Ejahbe eje ji á jo fili kehm gboko ejannge. Ane jo tokko nliki ebo tib go erem bi bo jo nyehn.
\v 11 Bo jo su Esowo bi li go ejahbetul tib go erem bi bo jo nyehn, a alok nya jo yam bo. Bo tikem yake abꞌbi abang ebo.
\p 
\v 12 Enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel erakera kehm yaange erakatahng ji Esowo ji woomo go ege ekpingi kak go aya ma nnen ma bo kpo lung re Yufrat. Alahb mao ka kpee, eji lꞌlim mbang ka atul ba li go ero nfam.
\p 
\v 13 N kehm nyehne esabsab etohko na ebra bi jolo go elfoongo ni akpajahme, jehko lohngo go nnyo mi edꞌragon,\f + \fr 16:13 \ft Ell 12:3\f* jehko lohngo go nnyo mi nnyam nyio,\f + \fr 16:13 \ft Ell 13:1\f* jehko lohngo go nnyo mi nkimfahnga nnyehnamahr.\f + \fr 16:13 \ft Ell 13:11\f*
\p 
\v 14 Bo jolo atohko nya eblehm nya kpo lim akpokosi. Bo kehm song kpiri atul ba li go njini kpee re, bo ko bo ba kono edi ajehng, eji bo lꞌba nok ebta go egburu efung bi Esowo bi gbale sehng.
\p 
\v 15 “Kunen ekpu! N kpꞌbake ana nwajv. Elfuulu bahke jolo ka nne no kil eblale, ye ji kpꞌkuuru abomo enye, eji á lꞌkꞌjen ebun ebun, ane jo rik-e ndon.”
\p 
\v 16 Atohko nyao ko atul bao ba a bo. Atul bao ba kono asi go edi ji bo jo lung go alum Hibru re Armagedon.
\p 
\v 17 Enjel nyehko nyi biingi enjel esehma kehm gohro yaange erakatahng ji Esowo ji woomo go ege ekpingi wohngo go ewuungu. N kehm soro wuk ellum ni bungu wahre wahre go eti etul ji jolo go etahk Esowo jio re, “Emmal!”
\p 
\v 18 Amangedu kehm kehme ellimi, a ewahl ane, aran jo ta, ndi jo gbꞌgbehke. Elkohn nio ka gbehka gbehke eji ane tiki li go njini. Jol njini ka gbehka gbehke ano.
\v 19 Egburu ejahbe kehm bahnge ejang ebra. Ajahbe kpee nya li go njini rannge kpee. Esowo kehm buumu Bebilon ji nnen a nnen, fere lim-e re, á wo go nkob amahm nyi egburu erakatahng eje.
\v 20 Ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji jolo go elka alahb daade kpee. Ewong ajehng ajehng kpeem jol, ji bo jo kpe nyehn.
\v 21 Agburu abahk elahb atal nya ebahk ajehng jo lub ana ekpa akang ji nnen jo fooro ero, jo tuubu ane. Ane kehm kehme Esowo su tib go erem bio bi elahb atal, tibre jolo egburu erem area.
\c 17
\s1 Njenasꞌsa no ga ga
\p 
\v 1 Enjel anyehng go ellong enjel nyio na esehma nyi fili nkpingi na esehma kehm bake, ba tong-m re, “Ba! M bahk-a tibi erem bi bo bahke kak njenasꞌsa no ga ga, ye ji jehk go ero alahb ma gbale gbal.
\v 2 Atul ba njini nyia noongo a njenasꞌsa noo.\f + \fr 17:2 \ft Jems 4:4\f* Ane ba li njini jo buumu amahm asꞌsa ma á ka bo, bo wo.”
\p 
\v 3 Enjel nyio kehm soro rod-m go etohko, tahm a name go elka emahng. Owo n kehm nyehne nnenkal jehk go mbilibila nnyam nyi abing akuk saab-e na saabe go ngubjing. Nnyam nyio bele esi na ebsehma, fere bel ntang ewubu.\f + \fr 17:3 \ft Ell 13:1\f*
\v 4 Nnenkal noo liibi abilibili nsol nya atul kpo kono elkake. Á liibi akpakamahr akpakamahr, eji á kake nsol nyi bo limi go agul, fere kak nsol nyi bo limi go atal nya nno a nno, fere kak amohkesol nya kpo sahb kꞌkim ekun. Á fili ekpingi agul go ebo ji nsol eltehb ma rur, a asabsab nsol nya asꞌsa enye.
\v 5 Go ege a mbuk, bo nyon-e nkpokosi a mbing re, “Bebilon ji gbale gbal, ye wo li ntul asꞌsa, a nfono eltehb go njini kpee.”
\v 6 N nyehne nnenkal noo kpꞌbuumu, tibre á jo wo alung ma aneb Esowo, fere jo wo alung ma ane ba bo wulu bo go esi ji Jisos. Eji n nyehn-e no, kpo-m esi sehng.
\p 
\v 7 Enjel nyio kehm-m bahbe re, “Jen ji wahnge kp-a kpoko esi? Nong, me n lennge nkpokosi nyi nnenkal noo tong-a, tob lennge bada nnyam nyio nyi solo nnenkal noo, nyi bele esi na ebsehma, a ntang ewubu.
\v 8 Nnyam nyio nyi a nyehne no, nyi jolo go elkpin ngare nyehko go, nyi ki kpe li go elkpin anv, á yahke ba ellohngo go nrabbe elbing nio ba. Á bahke feere song yel go ebi edi. Ane bao ba li go njini, ba bo ki nyon abing ebo go nwer nyi elkpin, njini kehm jolo, bahke kpoko bo esi sehng, bo lꞌnyehn nnyam nyio. Tibre á tohko jol go elkpin, anv, á kpeem li, á bahke kpe feere ba.
\p 
\v 9 “A wo li ntir elkahne. Asi nnyam nyio na asehma lohngo ewong na ebsehma bi nnenkal noo jehk no.
\v 10 Tob lohngo atul na asehma. Atul na alon kpeem li. Ntul awohng noa anv. Noko bahke kpe ba. Á lꞌba, á bahke jolo mmongare ntiil.
\v 11 Nnyam nyio nyi tohko jol go elkpin, anv, á ki kpe li, ye wo li ntul no bahke toono atul bao na asehma. Á tob wob go ellong atul bao na asehma. Á bahke yele go ebi edi.
\p 
\v 12 “Atang nyao na awubu nya a nyehne no, longo atul na awubu ba kala kehme adi fili. Bo bahke bele nsahm nyi bo bahke tobo nnyam nyio adi afili ana atul go awa anyehng.
\v 13 Bo li eltimtim anehng. Bo bahke faake a nsahm ebo, ka nnyam nyio, fere woom-e go elwo.
\v 14 Bo bahke noko ebta a mmon a njoro. Mmon a njoro, a ane ebe ba á lungu bo, fere jak bo, bo ji kpi ekakesehk kp-e toono, bahke gake bo. Tibre ye wo li ntul no sehnge atem atul bako kpee.”
\p 
\v 15 Enjel nyio kehm-m tongo re, “Alahb mao ma a nyehne no, ma nnenkal asꞌsa noo jehk go ero, lohngo ane, ellong ane gbalee, ajoobo ajahbe gbalee nya kpo bung alum ebo ebo.
\v 16 Ntang ewubu nyi a nyehne no, a nnyam nyio, bo bahke koko njenasꞌsa noo ekv, fere taar-e ejum ajehng ajehng ji á kpi no, yak-e ebun ebun. Bo bahke lehke ngubjing enye, fere fi-e agun.
\v 17 Tibre Esowo ebkak bo ntir nyio go bo a ntim re bo lim ji kp-e koro, fere jol eltimtim anehng, fere faake a etul ebo ka nnyam nyio tete alum nya Esowo bungu no lohko jol go etingitingi.
\p 
\v 18 “Nnenkal no a nyehn-e no, ye wo li egburu ejahbe ji atul ba li go njini wob-e go elwo.”
\c 18
\s1 Elgboko ni Bebilon gbo no
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn enjel nyehko kpꞌbadde go ejahbetul Esowo. Á jolo njꞌjok, fere bel nsahm. Ellub ene jo ka ellennge go njini.
\v 2 Á kehm rabe wahre wahre wahre re,
\q1 “Bebilon ji gbale gbal ebgbo! Bebilon ebgbo! Ebfere jol edi ellene ji eblehm. Esabsab etohko ajehng ajehng, a esabsab ebruk abehng abehng bi li ebruk eltehb lene elbad nio.\f + \fr 18:2 \ft Mat 13:32\f*
\q1 
\v 3 Tibre ane baka baka kpee ebwo amahm eme mao ma asꞌsa. Atul ba li go njini ebnoongo a ne. Ajenare ba njini nyia ebgbo afang tib go elfo ni á jo li.”
\p 
\v 4 Owo n kehm kpe wuk ellum nehko ni bungu go ejahbetul Esowo re,
\q1 “Lohngen ane ebame, lohngen o, eji ń lꞌkꞌyel go ege abiafem nya á kpꞌlimi, fere tob nyehn erem bi á bahke nyehne.\f + \fr 18:4 \ft 2 Kor 6:17\f*
\q1 
\v 5 Abiafem enye ebtub nsun, fere wahre elkul tete rehng go elbung. Esowo ebbuumu abꞌbi enye.
\q1 
\v 6 Tob limen ye ana á lim-n no. Bongen ye sehnge ana á limi no. Ganen ye amahm sehnge ana ma á ka-n no.
\q1 
\v 7 Ana á ka elne ellub, fere jo li elfo, ano wo fvfo ḿ bahke tob kak-e erem, fere lim-e, á jol ndon ndon.
\q1 
\v 8 Owo bahke wahnge erem bi á bahke nyehne bahke bake gburub efung abehng, erem behko bahke jolo elkv, behko ndon, behko njal.
\q1 Bo bahk-e fehke go agun. Tibre Jehova bi kp-e lame, kpꞌtahne.”
\p 
\v 9 Atul ba njini nyia ba noongo a ne, fere jo li elfo a ne, bo bahke jo ling, fere jo wa-e eyuu, eji bo bahke nyehne atꞌtohk nya ejahbe jio kpꞌlulu.\f + \fr 18:9 \ft Ell 2:22\f*
\v 10 Bo bahke jo yiimi dake dake, tibre bo kpꞌfahle erem bi á kpꞌnyehne. Bo bahke jo bung re,
\q1 “Eyuu a egburu ejahbe jio, Bebilon ji gbale gbal.
\q1 Re kehm biingi awa anyehng, erem eba ebba.”
\p 
\v 11 Abajenare ba li go njini nyia bahke jo ling. Eko bahke bo tan, tibre nnene limm, no kpꞌkpeke gunu nsol are ebo,
\v 12 agul, asilva, atal nya nno a nno, amohkesol nya kpo sahb kꞌkim ekun, anoobo abarebare abomo, abomo nya atul kpo kak a akal akal ebo, a afang ane, elkohn nti gbalee nyi kpo v eleenge, nsol nyi bo kpo ko amahn njok lim, nsol nyi bo kpo ko nti nyi kpo sahb kꞌkim ekun lim, abilikpi, akuungu, abarebare atal,
\v 13 nsol ana nyi bo kpo lung re esinamon, nyi bo kpo ko kak go nsol alehke yebe, alaknti ana nya bo kpo lung re mmir abola efrankinsens, nya bo kpo kak agun, jo teebe, jo v esꞌsvv eleenge, amahm, akehng, nkohl nyi bo kpo gok, lim abred, nsol atohkondi, ejoro, anyꞌnya, atꞌrok, aju, a atohko ane.
\p 
\v 14 Abajenare bao kehm-e tongo re, “Anoobo nsol nya a jo kunu ekpu re a bahke bele, ebdaade. Nsol afang enya kpee, a awiliwili nsol enya ebmal kpee, a nehm kpe ma bel.”
\p 
\v 15 Abajenare bo jo gungu nsol nyio, fere fang tib ye, bahke jo yiimi dake dake, tib bo bahke jo fahl erem bi á bahke jo nyehn. Bo bahke jo ling, fere jo wa-e eyuu wahre wahre re,
\v 16 “Eyuu, eyuu, eyuu a egburu ejahbe jia ji jo kono elliibi abarebare abomo, fere jo liibi abilibili nsol nya atul kpo kono elkake, fere jo kak nsol nyi bo limi go agul, fere tob jo kak nsol nyi bo limi go atal nya nno a nno, a amohkesol nya kpo sahb kꞌkim ekun.
\v 17 Re kehm biingi awa anyehng, nsol afang enye ebrannge kpee mal.”
\p Atubesi asohkkahng, go ane ba kpo lim eltum go asohkkahng, a ane bako kpee ba jo lim eltum go aya, bo jo yiimi dake dake,
\v 18 fere jo ling, eji bo nyehne atꞌtohk nya á jo lul. Bo kehm bungu re, “Ejahbe aji ji bik a egburu ejahbe jio?”
\p 
\v 19 Bo jo kpu ndi, jo kunu go bo asi, eji bo jo ling, fere jo wa eyuu re, “Eyuu a egburu ejahbe jio! Tib nsol afang nya ejahbe jio nya wahnge afono asohkkahng kpee gbo afang. Re kehm biingi awa anyehng, yebtane ejum ajehng ajehng kpee.”
\p 
\v 20 Aneb ejahbetul Esowo wahn, belen eyebatahng tib go ege elrannge. Belen eyebatahng, wahn aneb Esowo, a abatiingetib Jisos, go abanyehnamahr Esowo fvfo, tibre Esowo m-e lam, wahn fere li eno.
\p 
\v 21 Owo enjel nyi gbale gbal kehm mehle eltal ni jolo ana egburu eltal ngoko, tub kak agburu aya, kehm bungu re, “Ana wo bo bahke rodo egburu ejahbe ji bo kpo lung re Bebilon tub fvfo. Bo nehm kpe tiki nyehn enyehnenyehne.
\p 
\v 22 “Nnene limm, no bahke kpe wuk ase nya bo kpo kub go abuk ona, fere wuk afiri, a atang, fere wuk ase nya aneb ase kpꞌkubu. Nlimeltum awohng awohng ana ntahlagun, ana njammansol, ana nkonajangnti nehm kpe jol o ejolojolo. Nnene limm, no bahke kpe wuk nne awohng awohng kpꞌgoko nsol ona.
\v 23 Nnene limm, no bahke kpe nyehn etꞌrekahng ajehng ajehng kpꞌyake ona. Nnene limm, no bahke kpe je elkak elbal ona. Tibre abajenare eba ba jolo ajꞌjok ane kpee go njini. Go ega ntaane wo, a jo nehm ane kpee ba li go njini.”
\v 24 Alung aneb Esowo, a alung abanyehnamahr Esowo, a ma ane kpee ba bo wulu bo go njini, bo nyehne go ega ejahbe.\f + \fr 18:24 \ft Mat 23:35\f*
\c 19
\nb 
\v 1 Owo n kehm wuku ewahl ana alum ane gbalee go ejahbetul Esowo, ba jo bung wahre wahre re,
\q1 “Tehken Esowo! Eltahre, ellub, a nsahm li ka Esowo ebahre,
\q1 
\v 2 tibre elam eje ji á kpo lam, li go etingitingi, á kpo lam nob nob. Yeblam egburu njenasꞌsa noo no rannge njini nyia kpee go ege asꞌsa. Esowo m-e bongo tib goji á wulu alokeltum ebe.”
\m 
\v 3 Bo kehm kpe rabe nkpel nyehko re,
\q1 “Tehken Esowo! Tibre atꞌtohk nya kpꞌlohngo go ejahbe jio bahke jo je go ero go njinanjini.”
\p 
\v 4 Anebkul bao, eltahl ane ani, a enyam bio na eni, kehm gboko go ndi, kak Esowo bi jehk go eti etul jio re,
\q1 “Emen, tehken Esowo!”
\s1 Elkak elbal ni mmon a njoro
\p 
\v 5 N kehm wuku ellum ni bungu go eti etul jio re,
\q1 “Tehken Esowo ebahre, wahn alokeltum ebe kpee, ba kpo fahl-e, afi ń jolo anebkul, afi ń jolo abonse.”
\p 
\v 6 Owo n kehm kpe wuk ewahl ji jolo ana ewahl ji ane gbalee, fere jolo ana elahb ji kpꞌsahb wꞌwahl. Ewahl jio jolo ana aran nya kpꞌsahb tꞌta, nya bungu wahre wahre re,
\q1 “Tehken Esowo! Tibre Esowo Ntul ewahre no gbale sehng wo kpꞌfili edi.
\q1 
\v 7 Nong, wahr belen eyebatahng, fere jo geere. Nong, wahr ka-e ellub. Tibre ngare elbal nyi mmon a njoro bahke koko elbal ebbiingi. Nkal ewe ebtoobo ebjing.\f + \fr 19:7 \ft Mat 22:2; 25:1\f*
\q1 
\v 8 Bo tꞌtaame re, á liibi abarebare nsol nya kpꞌsahb bꞌbar kparaang.”
\m Tibre abarebare nsol nyao lohngo atingitingi nsol nya aneb Esowo limi no.
\p 
\v 9 Enjel nyio kehm bungu a name re, “Nyon nsol nyia re, Elfuulu bahke jolo ka ane ba bo ma tiingi bo elkak elbal nio ni mmon a njoro.”\f + \fr 19:9 \ft Luk 14:15\f* Enjel nyio kehm kpe bung a name re, “Atingitingi alum nya ana nya Esowo.”
\p 
\v 10 N kehm soro gbo go ege alata kak-e. Á kehm-m tongo re, “Ka kpe lim ano! Me n li nlokeltum ana wo, a abonane bako, ba kpo bung etingitingi ji Jisos lennge no ka bo. Jo kak Esowo!” Tibre, etingitingi ji Jisos lennge no ka, ji ji jolo abanyehnamahr Esowo go bo a ntim, bo jo bung.
\s1 Nne no kuumu go mbarebare enyꞌnya
\p 
\v 11 Owo n kehm nyehne mbu mi ejahbetul Esowo ma lennge. N kehm kpe nyehn mbarebare enyꞌnya. Nne no kuum-e go njahm, bo kpo lung-e re Nkakesehk a nne no li go etingitingi. Á kpo lam elam ji nno, fere jo nok ebta bi nno.
\v 12 Amahr enye li ana eblikagun. Á konngo akpasi atul gbalee. Á kpi mbing nyi bo nyon-e no, nyi nnene kil elkahne, sehngem ye ntahngtahng wo kpꞌkahne.
\v 13 Á kake ekpawobo ji bo nyobo go alung. Mbing enye, bo kpo lung-e re Alum Esowo.\f + \fr 19:13 \ft Jon 1:1,14\f*
\v 14 Nsoja nyi li go ejahbetul Esowo kehm tahme toon-e. Bo kake abarebare nsol nya sahb bꞌbar kparaang, fere kuumu go abarebare anyꞌnya.
\v 15 Ekongkong ekahngkahng kpo lohng-e go nnyo, bi á bahke koko, boomo ane ba li go njini. Á bahke jo fili bo go ebti bi bo limi go ekuungu. Á bahke kaame akab avain go elbing avain akaame ni egburu erakatahng ji Esowo bi gbale sehng.\f + \fr 19:15 \ft Ell 14:19-20\f*
\v 16 Bo nyono mbing go ege ekpawobo, fere nyon go ege eyo re, “Ntul no gbale sehnge atem atul bako.”\f + \fr 19:16 \ft 1 Tim 6:15\f*
\p 
\v 17 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn enjel nyehko yim go atahng njul. Á kehm rabe lung nruk kpee nyi jo fonngo go elka ejahbetul Esowo re, “Baan, wahn ba kono edi ajehng go egburu elkak ni Esowo,
\v 18 fere li akv atul, a akv nya atubesi nsoja, a nya ajꞌjok ane, fere tob li akpakv anyꞌnya, a akv nya ane ba jo kuumu bo go njahm, a nya ane kpee, afi bo jolo aju, afi aju bo jolem, afi bo jolo atul, afi bo jolo aja.”
\p 
\v 19 N nyehne nnyam nyio,\f + \fr 19:19 \ft Ell 13:1\f* a atul ba njini nyia, a nsoja ebo kpee. Bo kono edi ajehng re bo nok ebta a nne no kun go enyꞌnya, a nsoja enye.\f + \fr 19:19 \ft Ell 16:14,16\f*
\v 20 Bo kehm bobo nnyam nyio, a nkimfahnga nnyehnamahr no jo lim akpokosi go esamahr nnyam nyio. Tib go akpokosi nyao wo, á jo nehm ane ba bele elliingi ni nnyam nyio, fere jo nehm ane ba jo kak elokelom eje. Nnyam nyio, a nkimfahnga nnyehnamahr noo, bo ba, bo rodo bo mbir mbir, tub kak go eto agun ji asalfa kpo lul.
\v 21 Nsoja ebo kpee, nne no kuumu go enyꞌnya wulu bo kpee go ekahngkahng bi lohngo go ege a nnyo. Nruk nyio kpee kehm ba li akv ebo wohngo.
\c 20
\s1 Nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu (1,000)
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn enjel nyehko ma lohng go ejahbetul Esowo kpꞌbadde abake. Á fili egbokoro ji nrabbe elbing nio,\f + \fr 20:1 \ft 2 Pit 2:4; Jud 6; Ell 9:1\f* fere fili ngbekobo nyi nnen a nnen go ebo.
\v 2 Á kehm bobo edꞌragon jio ji li nkꞌkula nnyo, ye ji bo kpo lung-e re nnehm, fere jo lung-e re Nnekv, gbaang-e ngbekobo nyio re á jol ano go nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu.
\v 3 Owo á kehm-e rodo, tub kak nrabbe elbing nio, bulu, fere gbaange, eji á lꞌkꞌkpe nehm ane ba li go njini, tete biingi nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu. Lꞌbiingi ano, bo kehm-e yehke mmongare ntiil.
\p 
\v 4 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn nti etul, fere nyehn ane ba bo ka bo nsahm re bo jo lam alam jehk no go nti etul nyio. N kpe tob nyehn atohko nya ane ba bo kiimi bo asi tib go ntianse nyi bo jo yiimi ka Jisos, a alum Esowo. Bo tikem kak nnyam nyio, a elokelom eje. Bo tikem bel elliingi ene go bo a mbuk, jol go bo abo bo belem. Bo bele elkpin, fere jo fili edi a Kraist go nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu.\f + \fr 20:4 \ft Luk 22:30; 1 Kor 6:2\f*
\p 
\v 5 Akvne nyako kpeem nyahme, bel elkpin, tete nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu nyio biingi. A wo li ngbokambang elnyahme go elkv\f + \fr 20:5 \ft 1 Kor 15:23-24; 1 Tes 4:16\f*
\v 6 Ane ba bahke gboko mbang nyahme go elkv, bo ba li aneb Esowo, ba elfuulu ni Esowo li ka bo. Elkohn ane bao, etoono elkv, nsahm anyehng anyehng kpeem kpi nyi bahke kpe fili bo.\f + \fr 20:6 \ft Ell 20:14\f* Bo bahke jolo abalimajom ba Esowo, fere jol abalimajom ba Kraist. Bo bahke fili edi a ne go nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu.
\s1 Ebta bi bo bahke noko sehnge nnehm
\p 
\v 7 Eji ma biingi nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu, owo bo bahke yehke nnehm go ngbekobo nyi á woomo no yake.
\v 8 Á bahke lohngo ba nehm ane ba li go ejang njini abehng abehng. Bo ba li Gog abola Magog. Nnehm bahke lungu bo ba kono edi ajehng re bo nok ebta. Bo bahke ruru, are asahknti nya.
\p 
\v 9 Bo kehm yele, jo jen alab ejahbe tete ba sennge ebud aneb Esowo kak, a ejahbe ji kpo kor Esowo. Agun kehm lohngo go ejahbetul Esowo ba fi bo kpee.
\v 10 Nnehm nyi nehme bo, bo rod-e ro kak eto agun ji asalfa kpo lul, edi jio ji nnyam nyio, a nkimfahnga nnyehnamahr noo wob no. Owo bo bahke woomo, jo nyehn erem bi ebnohko atv a njul tete go njinanjini.
\s1 Esꞌkohro elam
\p 
\v 11 N kehm kpe nyehn egburu mbarebare eti etul, fere nyehn nne jehk no.\f + \fr 20:11 \ft Mat 25:31-32\f* Elbung abola ndi kehm beke go ege esamahr tahm. Edi ajehng ajehng kpeem jol ka bo, ji bo bahke jolo.\f + \fr 20:11 \ft 2 Pit 3:7,10,12\f*
\v 12 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn akvne, egom jindiki jolo abonse, egom jehko anebkul, bo yim go mbuksong eti etul jio. Esowo kehm lennge awer, kehm kpe lennge nwer nyehko nyi jolo nwer nyi elkpin.\f + \fr 20:12 \ft Fil 4:3\f* Akvne nyao, bo lame bo ana bo nyono go awer nyao, jang jang ana bo limi no.
\v 13 Agburu aya yake akvne nya woomo atahng ka. Elkv abola ejahbe akvne tob yake akvne nya bo fili no ka.\f + \fr 20:13 \ft Jon 5:28-29\f* Bo lame bo jang jang ana bo limi no.\f + \fr 20:13 \ft Rom 2:6\f*
\p 
\v 14 Elkv abola ejahbe akvne, bo rodo bo, ro kak go eto agun.\f + \fr 20:14 \ft 1 Kor 15:26\f* Eto agun jio ji li etoono elkv nehko.
\v 15 Nne awohng awohng no bo ki nyon mbing enye go nwer nyio nyi elkpin, bo rod-e na, ro kak go eto agun.\f + \fr 20:15 \ft Mat 25:41\f*
\c 21
\s1 Elbung ni nfenfe, a ndi nyi nfenfe
\p 
\v 1 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn elbung ni nfenfe, fere nyehn ndi nyi nfenfe.\f + \fr 21:1 \ft 2 Pit 3:13\f* Tibre ngbokambang elbung, a ngbokambang a ndi ebtan. Agburu aya kpeem li elikiliki.
\p 
\v 2 Owo n kehm kpe nyehn mbarebare ejahbe, Jeusalem ji nfenfe kpꞌbadde go ejahbetul Esowo abake.\f + \fr 21:2 \ft Hib 11:10,16\f* Á toobo ebjing, fere liibi ana nkalanne liibi re, á song kpiri nlumanne.\f + \fr 21:2 \ft Ell 19:7\f*
\v 3 N wuku ellum ni bungu wahre wahre go eti etul jio re, “Anv, Esowo bahke kake elsi ene goji ane. Á bahke lene tob bo. Bo bahke jolo ane ebe. Yefono antahng bahke jolo a bo, fere jol Esowo ebo.
\v 4 Á bahke fulu bo abonngo kpee go bo amahr. Elkv nehm kpe jol ejolojolo. Ndon anyehng anyehng nehm kpe jol. Aling nehm kpe jol. Ayam nehm kpe jol. Tibre nsol nyi tohko jol ebtan.”
\p 
\v 5 Nne no jehk go eti etul jio kehm bungu re, “Anv, n kpꞌlimi nsol kpee, fere jol nyi nfenfe.”\f + \fr 21:5 \ft 2 Kor 5:17\f* Á kpe bung re, “Nyon alum nyaa, tibre alum nyaa, alum etingitingi nya, li alum nya nne bahke bumu go etingitingi.”
\p 
\v 6 Á kehm-m tongo re, “Ebmal. Me wo li Alfa, me jꞌnehm wo li Omega. Me wo li mbomannahb, me jꞌnehm wo li esꞌkohlo. Nne no alahb lꞌkor-e, m bahk-e kake alahb mbol mbol, ma lohng go elbing alahb nio ni alahb ma elkpin.\f + \fr 21:6 \ft Jon 4:14\f*
\p 
\v 7 “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌga anebekv ebe, á bahke lehke elkv nia. M bahke jolo Esowo ebe, ye bahke jolo mmon ewame.\f + \fr 21:7 \ft Ell 2:7\f*
\v 8 Agubgub ane, ane ba kil jo taame, ane ba ma rannge, awulane, ane ba kpo noongo a ane, aneb ntaane, abajomeblom, akimfahnge ane kpee, nsehng ebo nyi bo bahke lehke, bo bahke woomo go eto ji asalfa kpo lul. Owo li etoono elkv nehko.”
\s1 Jeusalem ji nfenfe
\p 
\v 9 Enjel anyehng nyi woomo go ellong enjel na esehma nyi fili nkpingi na esehma bi esꞌkohro arem na asehma ruru no, kehm bake go egame, ba tong-m re, “Ba, me n song tib-a nkal a mmon a njoro.”\f + \fr 21:9 \ft Ell 19:7\f*
\p 
\v 10 Á kehm-m rodo go etohko, tahm a name go ewong ji sahb wꞌwahre, fere tib-m Jeusalem, mbarebare ejahbe kpꞌbadde go ejahbetul Esowo abake.
\v 11 Bele ellub ni Esowo, fere jo ya ana eltal ni nno a nno ni ga ga, ni li ana eltal ni bo kpo lung re ejaspa, fere wili ana eltal ni bo kpo lung re ekristel.
\v 12 Bele egburu ekahme sennge kak, ji wahre wahre. Ekahme jio bele ewubu a mbutahk ebal. Ewubu enjel ebal jolo go abutahk nyao. Go abutahk nyao, bo nyono ewubu a mbing ebal nyi atꞌtohngo nya li go Israel kpee.\f + \fr 21:12 \ft Ell 7:5-8\f*
\v 13 Ekahme jio bele ngoongo eni, ejang ajehng ajehng jo bele mbutahk era, ejang ero nfam bele mbutahk era, ejang erede nfam bele mbutahk era, ejang eboblum bele mbutahk era, ejang ebobkal bele mbutahk era.
\v 14 Ekahme ji ejahbe jio bele ewubu atal abal nya bo ko bum nnahb ekahme. Atal nyao, bo nyono abing abatiingetib mmon a njoro, ewubu ane abal.\f + \fr 21:14 \ft Ef 2:20\f*
\p 
\v 15 Nne no jo bung a name fili ejum ana ejiingi ji bo limi go agul re á ba gare ejahbe jio, fere gare abu, fere tob gare ekahme.
\v 16 Ejahbe jio bele ngoongo eni. Alab, a akpang jolo jang jang. Enjel nyio jo gare ejahbe jio go ege ejiingi. Jolo astadio gbalee (12,000), nya li ejum mmal atahltahl nkpel era atahlku.
\v 17 Á tob gare ekahme fvfo, wahre sehnge ana njan, jolo akubit atahl asehma a ekubit emni (144). (Ekubit ajehng li erula ajehng kunu esi). Enjel nyio gare ana nne kpo kono elgare.\f + \fr 21:17 \ft Jon 14:2\f*
\p 
\v 18 Bo lange ekahme jio go atal nya nno a nno, nya bo kpo lung re ejaspa. Yefono ejahbe, bo limi go nnyam agul agul, jo wili ana enyehn.
\v 19 Nnahb ekahme nyio, bo liibi go ajoobo atal nya nno a nno. Ngbokambang eltal jolo eltal ni bo kpo lung re ejaspa, nehko esafir, nehko agate, nehko emerald,
\v 20 nehko oniks, nehko ekarnilian, nehko ekrisolit, nehko eberil, nehko etopas, nehko ekrisopras, nehko ejasin, nehko ametist.
\v 21 Ewubu a mbutahk ebal mi jolo ewubu a mmohkesol ebal nya kpo sahb kꞌkim ekun. Mbu amehng amehng bo jo ko mmohkesol anyehng lim. Mbang nyi li go alab ejahbe jio jolo nnyam agul agul, jolo ana enyehn ji nne kpꞌnyehne wane go wane ga.
\p 
\v 22 Etahk Esowo ajehng ajehng nyehnem ejahbe jio. Tibre Jehova antahng antahng no gbale sehng, a mmon a njoro, bo ba li etahk Esowo ji ejahbe jio.
\v 23 Ejahbe jio ona kpehme seb njul, a ebareka re jo ya ona, tibre ellub ni Esowo ni kpꞌyake ejahbe jio, ni ni kpo ka ejahbe jio ellennge. Mmon a njoro wo li etꞌrekahng ji kpꞌyake ona.
\v 24 Ellennge nio ni mmon a njoro ni bahke wahnge ane baka baka ba li go njini nyia jo nyehn, fere jo jen.\f + \fr 21:24 \ft Mat 25:34\f* Atul ba li go njini nyia bahke koko ellub ebo ba a ni go ejahbe jio.
\v 25 Abu nya ejahbe jio, bo nehm jo tiki bam. Bahke jo jol foong efung kohro kohro. Atv nehm kpe jol o ejolojolo.
\v 26 Ane baka baka kpee ba li go njini bahke jo ko ellub ebo ba a ni go ejahbe jio, a ekpunu ebo.
\v 27 Ejumjum nehm yel ejahbe jio ji ki li saang. Nnene limm, no bahke yele ejahbe jio, no kpo lim nsol eltehb, afi á kpo kiimi afahnge, sehngem ane ba, bo nyono abing ebo go nwer nyi elkpin nyi mmon a njoro, bo ba bahke yele ejahbe jio.
\c 22
\nb 
\v 1 Owo á kehm-m tibi aya ma alahb elkpin, ma jo wili ana eltal ni bo kpo lung re ekristel, bomo elfabe go eti etul ji Esowo, a ji mmon a njoro,
\v 2 asongo go elka mbang ni ejahbe jio. Eti ji elkpin yiimi go egbuk aya ebbal ebbal.\f + \fr 22:2 \ft Ell 2:7\f* Jo kabe akab, ewubu a nkpel ebal go elya, nkpel anyehng go nnyahng. Anyane eti nyao nya li ekahm ji ane baka baka ba li go njini.\f + \fr 22:2 \ft Ell 21:24\f*
\p 
\v 3 Ejum nkuk ajehng ajehng nehm jo jol go ejahbe jio. Eti etul ji Esowo, jꞌnehm ji li ji mmon a njoro bahke jolo o. Alokeltum ebe bahke jo kak-e.
\v 4 Bo bahke jo nyehn esamahr ebe.\f + \fr 22:4 \ft Mat 5:8\f* Mbing enye bahke jolo go bo a mbuk.
\v 5 Atv nehm kpe jol ejolojolo. Bo nehm kpe seb atꞌrekahng, jol njul bo nehm kpe seb. Tibre Jehova wo bahke jolo etꞌrekahng ebo ji bahke jo ka bo ellennge. Bo bahke jolo atul, jo fili adi go njinanjini.
\s1 Elbake ni Jisos bahke bake
\p 
\v 6 Á kehm-m tongo re, “Alum nyaa, alum etingitingi nya, li alum nya nne bahke bumu go etingitingi. Jehova no kpo ka abanyehnamahr ebe etohko eje, ye wo ma tum enjel enye re á ba tib alokeltum ebe ejum ji bahke gulu ellimi.”
\p 
\v 7 Jisos bungu re, “Wuungen atung! N kpꞌbake go elwaare! Elfuulu bahke jolo ka nne no jo bum alum enyehnamahr nya nwer nyia.”
\p 
\v 8 Me Jon wo, ji wuku nsol nyia, fere nyꞌnyehn. N wuku kan nsol nyia, fere nyꞌnyehn, n kehm gboko jamme enjel nyi tib-m nsol nyia alahng re me n kak-e.
\p 
\v 9 Enjel nyio kehm-m tongo re, “Nobem re wo lim ano. Jo kak Esowo.\f + \fr 22:9 \ft Elt 10:26\f* Me n tob li nlokeltum ana wo, a abonane ba li abanyehnamahr, a ane ba kpo bum alum nya nwer nyia.”
\p 
\v 10 Á kehm-m kpe tong re, “Ka bulu nwer nyia nyi alum enyehnamahr Esowo wob no, tibre ngare ebkabbe.
\v 11 Nong, aneb abꞌbi jo lim abꞌbi, aneb eltehb sa ano go bo eltehb. Nong, anobonobo ane jo lim nob nob. Nong, ane ba li saang sa ano saang.”
\p 
\v 12 Jisos kpe bung re, “Kpuren, n kpꞌbake go elwaare. M bahke koko eltuuru ename ba a ni ba tuuru nne awohng awohng ana á limi no.\f + \fr 22:12 \ft Rom 2:6\f*
\v 13 Me wo li Alfa, me jꞌnehm wo li Omega. Me wo li ngbokambang, me jꞌnehm wo li nkahlanjahm. Me wo li mbomannahb, me jꞌnehm wo li esꞌkohlo.
\p 
\v 14 “Elfuulu bahke jolo ka ane bao ba kpo ru akpawobo ebo saang, eji bo lꞌbel nsahm nyi bo bahke ma li akab nyao nya eti ji elkpin, fere bel nsahm nyi bo bahke ma sehng go abutahk nyao yel ejahbe jio.
\v 15 Ane ba lꞌkꞌjol ejahbe jio, bo ba li ebv,\f + \fr 22:15 \ft Mat 7:6; Fil 3:2\f* aneb ntaane, ane ba kpo noongo a ane, awulane, abajomeblom,\f + \fr 22:15 \ft 1 Kor 6:9-10\f* akimfahnge ane, a nne awohng awohng no afahnge kpo kor-e.
\p 
\v 16 “Me Jisos, me wo ma tum enjel enyame tv-n re á ba yiimi ntianse go nsol nyia tong wahn aneb ero. Me wo li nlohk nyi Devid. Me n tob li nne no lohng go ege etꞌtohngo. Me wo li elonlo ji efungfu ji kpo sahb yꞌya.”
\p 
\v 17 Etingi Etohko, a nkalanne, bo kpo bung re, “Ba!”\f + \fr 22:17 \ft Rom 8:23\f* Nong, nne awohng awohng no lꞌwuk ellum nia tob bung re, “Ba!” Nong, ye ji alahb m-e kor, á ba, ba ko alahb ma elkpin mbol mbol, nne awohng awohng no lꞌfere kor-e.\f + \fr 22:17 \ft Jon 7:37\f*
\s1 Ana Jon rehke ane
\p 
\v 18 N kpꞌrehke nne awohng awohng no lꞌwuk alum enyehnamahr nya wob nwer nyia re, Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbudu ejum ajehng ajehng go alum nyaa, Esowo bahk-e budu erem ana bi bo nyono go nwer nyia.
\v 19 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌyehke ellum anehng anehng go alum enyehnamahr nya wob nwer nyia, Esowo bahk-e taare nsahm nyi kehn á jol lehke akab nti nyao nya li go eti ji elkpin, fere taar-e nsahm nyi kehn á jol bele re á lene go mbarebare ejahbe jio ji bo nyono go nwer nyia.\f + \fr 22:19 \ft Mat 5:18\f*
\p 
\v 20 Ye ji kpꞌyiimi ntianse go nsol nyia kpꞌbungu re, “Etingitingi, n kpꞌbake elwaare.” Emen. Ba, Ntul a Jisos!\f + \fr 22:20 \ft 1 Jon 3:3\f*
\p 
\v 21 Nong, nnoobo nyi Ntul a Jisos Kraist jol a aneb Esowo kpee. Emen.
